%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Viral%20videos%20of%20EVs%20catching%20fire%20after%20Hurricane%20Helene%20raise%20safety%20concerns%20in%20Florida%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Tesla%20that%20exploded%20after%20being%20inundated%20with%20salt%20water%20from%20Hurricane%20Helene%20sits%20in%20a%20parking%20lot%20in%20St.%20Pete%20Beach%2C%20Florida%2C%20on%20September%2028%2C%202024.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66fe113f5ccfc192a552cb36%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Tesla%20that%20caught%20fire%20during%20Hurricane%20Helene%20in%20St.%20Pete%20Beach%2C%20Florida%2C%20on%20September%2028%2C%202024.%3Cp%3ETed%20Richardson%2FThe%20Washington%20Post%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EHurricane%20Helene%20caused%20at%20least%206%20EV%20fires%20in%20Florida%2C%20according%20to%20state%20officials.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESaltwater%20can%20corrode%20lithium-ion%20batteries%2C%20leading%20to%20short-circuits%20and%20fires.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFlorida%20officials%20are%20pressuring%20EV%20makers%20to%20notify%20customers%20about%20the%20risks.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20Hurricane%20Helene%20barreled%20into%20northwestern%20Florida%2C%20local%20government%20officials%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D1886706438505288%26ref%3Dsharing%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshared%20footage%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20an%20electric%20vehicle%20catching%20fire%20in%20a%20flooded%20garage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20video%2C%20posted%20by%20Pinellas%20County%20officials%20on%20social%20media%2C%20came%20with%20a%20warning%20for%20EV%20owners%20about%20the%20risks%20posed%20by%20salt%20water%2C%20which%20can%20corrode%20lithium-ion%20batteries%20and%20cause%20them%20to%20short-circuit%20and%20overheat.%20Don't%20%26quot%3Bcharge%2C%20drive%2C%20or%20store%20your%20EV%20or%20E-bike%20in%20your%20home%20or%20garage%2C%26quot%3Bthe%20post%20said.%20It%20recommended%20they%20%26quot%3Bmove%20the%20EV%20or%20E-bike%2050%20feet%20away%20from%20any%20other%20combustible%20material%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bhave%20the%20vehicle%20towed%20to%20a%20dealership%20for%20inspection.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplatform.twitter.com%2Fwidgets.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22twitter%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EElectric%20Vehicles%20that%20have%20been%20flooded%20in%20saltwater%20can%20catch%20fire.%20If%20you%20evacuated%20and%20left%20an%20electric%20vehicle%20or%20golf%20cart%20in%20your%20garage%20or%20under%20a%20building%20and%20you%20are%20not%20able%20to%20get%20to%20it%20or%20move%20it%2C%20we%20want%20you%20to%20let%20us%20know.%20%2F1%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FdpfiXRAGuR%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FdpfiXRAGuR%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Pinellas%20County%20(%40PinellasGov)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPinellasGov%2Fstatus%2F1840042408832045266%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%2028%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EFlorida%20officials%20said%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20they%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmyfloridacfo.com%2Fnews%2Fpressreleases%2Fpress-release-details%2F2024%2F10%2F02%2Ffire-safety-alert-cfo---state-fire-marshal-jimmy-patronis--lithium-ion-batteries-are-ticking-time-bombs-in-wake-of-hurricane-helene%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esince%20confirmed%2016%20lithium-ion-battery%20fires%3C%2Fa%3E%20related%20to%20Hurricane%20Helene's%20storm%20surge%2C%20six%20of%20which%20were%20in%20EVs.%20Electric%20golf%20carts%2C%20e-bikes%2C%20and%20other%20battery-powered%20devices%20are%20also%20a%20hazard.%20The%20fires%20led%20Florida's%20chief%20financial%20officer%20and%20fire%20marshal%2C%20Jimmy%20Patronis%2C%20to%20call%20on%20automakers%20to%20be%20more%20proactive%20about%20notifying%20customers%20about%20moving%20their%20EVs%20to%20higher%20ground%20ahead%20of%20a%20storm%20(as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhurricane-helene-electric-vehicles-evs-owners-fire-risk-safety-tips-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGov.%20Ron%20DeSantis%3C%2Fa%3E%20did%20before%20Helene%20arrived)%20and%20about%20what%20to%20do%20if%20an%20EV%20is%20flooded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20too%20late%20for%20these%20manufacturers%20to%20send%20out%20notifications%20and%20fire%20safety%20information%20directly%20to%20their%20consumers%2C%26quot%3B%20Patronis%20said%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20adding%20that%20his%20office%20was%20coordinating%20with%20emergency%20responders%20to%20make%20residents%20aware%20of%20the%20risks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20warnings%20come%20at%20a%20critical%20time%20for%20the%20EV%20industry.%20Consumer%20demand%20for%20EVs%20has%20been%20slower%20than%20expected%20this%20year%2C%20and%20Republicans%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjd-vance-elon-musk-tesla-electric-vehicle-tax-credit-oil-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJD%20Vance%20have%20attacked%20the%20industry%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20presidential%20election%20in%20November.%20J.D.%20Power%20has%20forecast%20that%20EVs%20will%20account%20for%209%25%20of%20the%20market%20this%20year%20%E2%80%94%20a%20figure%20the%20group%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jdpower.com%2Fbusiness%2Fresources%2Fjd-power-revises-ev-retail-share-forecast%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erevised%20down%20from%2012%25%20because%20of%20slower%20adoption%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Surveys%20have%20suggested%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fev-charging-range-improving-americans-still-dont-want-electric-cars-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmericans%20are%20a%20lot%20more%20concerned%20about%20finding%20chargers%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20safety%2C%20but%20viral%20videos%20of%20EV%20fires%20could%20fuel%20skepticism.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrent%20Gruber%2C%20the%20executive%20director%20of%20J.D.%20Power's%20electric-vehicle%20practice%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20because%20of%20the%20recent%20fires%2C%20his%20team%20planned%20to%20begin%20tracking%20consumers'%20concern%20about%20EV%20fires.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20data%20from%20the%20Transportation%20Department%20and%20Tesla%20suggests%20EVs%20catch%20fire%20less%20often%20than%20hybrid%20or%20gas-powered%20cars%20on%20the%20road%20or%20in%20crashes.%20Saltwater%20storm%20surges%20during%20Hurricanes%20Ida%2C%20Ian%2C%20and%20now%20Helene%20pose%20a%20risk%20to%20lithium-ion%20batteries%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20clear%20how%20often%20EV%20fires%20occur%20during%20extreme%20weather%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20National%20Highway%20Traffic%20Safety%20Administration%20said%20its%20data%20on%20vehicle%20fires%20was%20limited%20to%20fires%20after%20fatal%20crashes.%20The%20agency%20said%20that%20since%20Hurricane%20Ian%20struck%20Florida%20in%202022%2C%20it%20has%20monitored%20reports%20of%20EV%20fires%20during%20coastal%20storms%20in%20the%20southeastern%20and%20northeastern%20US%20and%20in%20California.%20It%20said%20reports%20of%20EV%20fires%20resulting%20from%20saltwater%20flooding%20came%20only%20from%20Florida.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMore%20research%20is%20underway%20to%20better%20understand%20the%20interaction%20of%20high-voltage%20battery%20systems%20and%20saltwater%20immersion%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%20They%20added%20that%20the%20agency%20had%20proposed%20updating%20some%20safety%20requirements%20for%20EV%20batteries%20to%20reduce%20the%20risk%20of%20these%20fires.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlbert%20Gore%2C%20the%20executive%20director%20of%20the%20Zero%20Emission%20Transportation%20Association%2C%20which%20represents%20EV%20makers%20like%20Tesla%20and%20Rivian%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20manufacturers%20had%20done%20a%20lot%20of%20outreach%20over%20the%20past%20decade%20to%20local%20fire%20departments%20about%20EV-battery%20safety.%20He%20emphasized%20that%20the%20fires%20seemed%20to%20be%20limited%20to%20coastal%20regions%20where%20saltwater%20storm%20surge%20is%20a%20risk%20and%20argued%20that%20EVs%20in%20general%20are%20much%20less%20likely%20to%20catch%20fire%20than%20gas-powered%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20most%20important%20piece%20of%20information%20to%20communicate%20is%20if%20you%20live%20in%20an%20area%20where%20there's%20a%20risk%20of%20hurricanes%20and%20storm%20surge%2C%20it's%20really%20important%20to%20move%20that%20vehicle%20to%20higher%20ground%2C%26quot%3B%20Gore%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20fire%20departments%20along%20Florida's%20coastline%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20they'd%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felectric-vehicle-fires-what-to-know-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeducating%20their%20emergency%20responders%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20public%20about%20how%20to%20prevent%20and%20put%20out%20EV%20fires%20since%20Hurricane%20Ian%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKelsey%20Grentzer%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20government%20in%20Pinellas%20County%2C%20which%20covers%20St.%20Petersburg%20and%20Clearwater%2C%20said%20that%20so%20far%20during%20Hurricane%20Helene%2C%20emergency%20responders%20in%20the%20county%20had%20been%20called%20out%20to%20at%20least%2093%20vehicle%20fires.%20Grentzer%20said%20they%20were%20still%20analyzing%20the%20breakdown%20of%20how%20many%20were%20gas%20cars%20versus%20EVs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHeather%20Mazurkiewicz%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20North%20Collier%20Fire%20Control%20and%20Rescue%20District%2C%20which%20covers%20Naples%2C%20didn't%20have%20an%20exact%20figure%20for%20Helene%20but%20said%20the%20district%20had%20been%20taking%20the%20problem%20seriously.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20predictability%20as%20to%20how%20or%20when%20a%20fire%20will%20start%20from%20the%20battery%20compartment.%20They're%20extremely%20volatile%2C%26quot%3B%20Mazurkiewicz%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20after%20an%20EV%20battery%20fire%20appears%20to%20be%20extinguished%2C%20lingering%20stored%20energy%20can%20cause%20what's%20known%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bthermal%20runaway%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20cycle%20of%20overheating%20and%20over-pressurizing.%20Putting%20out%20the%20battery%20fire%20can%20require%20more%20than%2010%2C0000%20gallons%20of%20water%2C%20Mazurkiewicz%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20volatility%20was%20on%20display%20in%20the%20Pinellas%20County%20officials'%20viral%20video.%20The%20EV%20owners%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fox13news.com%2Fnews%2Felectric-vehicle-catches-fire-garage-destroys-home-during-hurricane-helene%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20a%20local%20Fox%20affiliate%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20they%20narrowly%20escaped%20their%20home%20in%20Siesta%20Key%20as%20it%20became%20engulfed%20in%20flames%20and%20that%20they%20didn't%20know%20that%20a%20small%20amount%20of%20flooding%20could%20ignite%20the%20EV.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflorida-ev-battery-fires-safety-hurricane-helene-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727954789000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66fe14db9e0c5c2eeeea3d9c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflorida-ev-battery-fires-safety-hurricane-helene-2024-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Florida%20officials%20confirmed%2016%20lithium-ion-battery%20fires%20related%20to%20Hurricane%20Helene's%20storm%20surge%2C%20six%20of%20which%20were%20in%20electric%20vehicles.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22cboudreau%40insider.com%20(Catherine%20Boudreau)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonic