%2C%20Goldfarb%20says%20she%20is%20%26quot%3Bconfident%20it%20will%20be%20full.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20hope%20as%20a%20strategy%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added%2C%20noting%20that%20half%20of%20the%20project%20was%20pre-leased%20to%20the%20law%20firm%20Crowell%20%26amp%3B%20Morning.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20based%20on%20real%20data%20and%20real%20activity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAcross%20the%20country%2C%20major%20office%20markets%20from%20New%20York%20to%20San%20Francisco%20have%20been%20pummeled%20by%20the%20lasting%20popularity%20of%20remote%20and%20hybrid%20work.%20Newly%20built%2C%20high-end%20offices%2C%20however%2C%20are%20finding%20takers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20demand%20has%20persisted%20even%20as%20office%20construction%20has%20been%20stifled%20by%20higher%20interest%20rates%20and%20inflation%2C%20which%20have%20pushed%20up%20costs.%20Worries%20over%20the%20health%20of%20the%20office%20market%20have%20also%20made%20lenders%20reluctant%20to%20finance%20new%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%2030%20million%20square%20feet%20of%20new%20office%20space%20will%20be%20completed%20this%20year%20in%20the%20US%2C%20roughly%20half%20of%20what%20was%20built%20in%202019%2C%20before%20the%20pandemic%2C%20says%20CBRE%2C%20the%20real%20estate%20services%20firm.%20In%202025%2C%20deliveries%20will%20fall%20even%20further%2C%20to%2014%20million%20square%20feet%2C%20CBRE%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20overall%20office%20market%20is%20awash%20in%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20square%20feet%20of%20empty%20space%2C%20CBRE%20predicts%20that%20vacancy%20in%20the%20market's%20upper%20segment%20will%20drop%20to%20pre-pandemic%20levels%20by%202027%20%E2%80%93%20around%20the%20same%20time%20projects%20that%20are%20breaking%20ground%20now%20will%20be%20ready.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20growing%20number%20of%20office%20developers%20have%20taken%20notice%20and%20see%20a%20budding%20shortage%20they%20are%20eager%20to%20cater%20to.%20Large%20office%20tenants%2C%20who%20often%20plan%20their%20space%20decisions%20years%20in%20advance%2C%20have%20also%20begun%20to%20recognize%20that%20while%20space%20options%20may%20abound%20now%2C%20they%20are%20likely%20to%20vanish%20in%20the%20coming%20years%20%E2%80%93%20raising%20interest%20in%20new%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20last%20six%2C%20seven%20months%2C%20there's%20not%20just%20people%20coming%20kicking%20the%20tires%2C%20there's%20people%20that%20are%20really%20looking%20to%20engage%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Scott%20Rechler%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20RXR%20Realty%2C%20referring%20to%20what%20he%20says%20is%20growing%20tenant%20interest%20in%20175%20Park%20Ave.%2C%20a%202.8-million-square-foot%20skyscraper%20designed%20by%20Skidmore%2C%20Owings%20%26amp%3B%20Merrill%20that%20developers%20RXR%20and%20TF%20Cornerstone%20are%20planning%20next%20to%20Grand%20Central%20Terminal%20in%20midtown%20Manhattan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20group%20now%20aims%20to%20begin%20construction%20on%20the%20more%20than%20%244%20billion%2C%201%2C575-foot-tall%20tower%20midway%20through%202025%20and%20with%20significantly%20less%20pre-leasing%20than%20originally%20planned%20because%20of%20their%20growing%20confidence%20in%20demand.%20Asking%20rents%20at%20the%20tower%20will%20be%20above%20%24200%20per%20square%20foot%2C%20among%20the%20highest%20ever%20sought%20in%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20used%20to%20be%20a%20point%20where%20we%20thought%20we%20would%20need%20to%20pre-lease%20all%20of%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Rechler%20said.%20%26quot%3BNow%2C%20we%20think%20that%20at%20500%2C000%20feet%2C%20it's%20probably%20enough%20to%20get%20going.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERechler%20said%20that%20interest%20in%20elite%20new%20space%20had%20been%20stoked%20by%20other%20high-end%20offerings%20in%20the%20market%2C%20such%20as%20One%20Vanderbilt%2C%20a%20recently%20built%20nearby%20tower%2C%20JPMorgan's%20new%20headquarters%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjpmorgan-nyc-headquarters-design-270-park-avenue-request-proposals-2021-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E270%20Park%20Ave.%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20a%20planned%20skyscraper%20at%20350%20Park%20Ave.%20that%20will%20house%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fken-griffin-citadel-office-space-real-estate-fifth-avenue-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einvestment%20firm%20Citadel%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20your%20competitors%20have%20a%20building%20like%20that%20that%20they're%20identified%20with%20and%20you're%20trying%20to%20be%20on%20a%20parallel%20path%2C%20you're%20going%20to%20say%20I%20want%20to%20be%20in%20a%20space%20at%20the%20same%20level%20or%20better%2C%26quot%3B%20Rechler%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Large%20conference%20room%20and%20office%20space%20overlooking%20Midtown%20Manhattan.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66fd8efb5ccfc192a552a9ab%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221852%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20rendering%20of%20the%20North%20East%20Terrace%20at%20the%20planned%2070%20Hudson%20Yards%20office%20building.%3Cp%3ERelated%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225d3faa99-284e-4185-804a-807a2344cd11%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EOther%20developers%20are%20laying%20plans%20for%20new%20towers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20large%20development%20firm%20Related%20Companies%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20says%20that%20four%20office%20towers%20it%20has%20built%20with%20Oxford%20Properties%20as%20part%20of%20their%20Hudson%20Yards%20mega-project%2C%20are%20now%2099%25%20full.%20The%20team%20is%20readying%20to%20begin%20a%20new%2045-story%2C%201.1-million-square-foot%20office%20property%20called%2070%20Hudson%20Yards%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20think%20we're%20going%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20only%20new%20buildings%20in%20'27%2C%20'28%20when%20there's%20going%20to%20be%20no%20new%20supply%2C%26quot%3B%20Philippe%20Visser%2C%20Related's%20president%20of%20office%20development%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20overall%20office%20vacancy%20is%20now%20at%2015.1%25%20in%20Manhattan%2C%20according%20to%20CBRE%2C%20Visser%20sees%20little%20competition%20between%20the%20overwhelming%20majority%20of%20that%20empty%20space%20and%20Hudson%20Yards%2C%20where%20a%20number%20of%20major%20corporate%20names%20have%20migrated%20in%20recent%20years%20to%20take%20occupancy%20of%20newly%20built%20buildings.%20Tenants%20include%20Wells%20Fargo%2C%20KKR%2C%20BlackRock%2C%20Meta%2C%20and%20L'Or%C3%A9al.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20these%20successful%20companies%20who%20are%20looking%20for%20really%20dynamic%20office%20space%20want%20new%20construction%2C%26quot%3B%20Visser%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E70%20Hudson%20Yards%20will%20feature%20an%20array%20of%20state-of-the-art%20features%2C%20including%20a%20triple-paned%20glass%20facade%2C%20which%20greatly%20enhances%20the%20insulating%20properties%20of%20glass%20exteriors%20and%20will%20make%20the%20building%20more%20energy%20efficient%20and%20appealing%20to%20sustainability-conscious%20office%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Lower%20Manhattan%2C%20Larry%20Silverstein%20hinted%20that%20he%20is%20close%20to%20moving%20ahead%20with%20plans%20to%20erect%20the%20final%20office%20skyscraper%20at%20the%20World%20Trade%20Center%2C%20a%202.8%20million-square-foot%20tower%20designed%20by%20architect%20Norman%20Foster.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERumors%20abound%20that%20Silverstein%20is%20close%20to%20signing%20a%20large%20lease%20with%20American%20Express%20that%20would%20allow%20the%20project%20to%20proceed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20stay%20tuned%26quot%3B%20was%20all%20Silverstein%20would%20say%20about%20the%20possible%20deal%20at%20the%20tower%2C%202%20World%20Trade%20Center.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESilverstein%20said%20he%20was%20certain%20other%20tenants%20would%20fill%20up%20the%20remainder%20of%20the%20building's%20available%20space%20once%20construction%20is%20underway.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20put%20everything%20this%20buildings%20has%20all%20together%2C%20it's%20superior%2C%26quot%3B%20Silverstein%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20never%20left%20my%20mind%20that%20someday%20we%20would%20succeed%20in%20accomplishing%20Tower%202%20%E2%80%93%20and%20that's%20where%20we%20are%20today.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EManhattan%20is%20particularly%20conducive%20to%20new%20construction%20in%20that%20it%20has%20both%20a%20large%20captive%20audience%20of%20corporate%20office%20users%20and%20a%20deep%20inventory%20of%20old%2C%20outdated%20office%20properties%20that%20have%20fallen%20out%20of%20favor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20because%20there%20is%20so%20little%20office%20construction%20on%20the%20horizon%20nationally%2C%20builders%20have%20begun%20to%20lay%20similar%20plans%20in%20other%20markets%20with%20similar%20dynamics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVisser%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20says%20Related%20expects%20to%20break%20ground%20on%20a%20new%2040-story%2C%20925%2C000-square-foot%20office%20tower%20at%20725%20W.%20Randolph%20St.%20in%20Chicago%20by%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20that%20city%20is%20also%20awash%20in%20available%20space%2C%20the%20building%20would%20be%20one%20of%20the%20only%20available%20newly%20built%20office%20properties%20in%20the%20Fulton%20Market%20neighborhood%2C%20a%20desirable%20sub-district%20in%20the%20city's%20West%20Loop%20that%20is%20known%20for%20its%20retail%20and%20restaurants%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERelated%20Ross%2C%20a%20spinoff%20development%20firm%20launched%20earlier%20this%20year%20by%20Related's%20founder%2C%20Stephen%20Ross%2C%20is%20about%20to%20begin%20construction%20on%2015%20City%20Place%2C%20a%20nearly%20500%2C000-square-foot%20office%20building%20in%20West%20Palm%20Beach%2C%20Florida.%20The%20project%20is%20about%2070%25%20pre-leased%20to%20an%20undisclosed%20roster%20of%20tenants%2C%20according%20to%20Jordan%20Rathlev%2C%20a%20senior%20vice%20president%20of%20development%20at%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERathlev%20said%20he%20recently%20received%20a%20space%20inquiry%20from%20a%20financial%20technology%20firm%20that%20is%20seeking%20at%20least%20300%2C000%20square%20feet%20%E2%80%93%20far%20more%20than%2015%20City%20Place%20can%20accommodate.%20The%20interest%20from%20that%20tenant%20and%20others%20has%20given%20a%20boost%20to%20the%20company's%20ambitions%20to%20begin%20building%20a%20neighboring%20office%20property%20called%2010%20City%20Place%20that%20will%20also%20be%20around%20500%2C000%20square%20feet%20in%20size.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20intent%20is%20that%20they're%20both%20going%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Rathlev%20said%2C%20indicating%20Related's%20hope%20that%20it%20will%20sign%20enough%20anchor%20tenancy%20at%2010%20City%20Place%20to%20build%20it%20and%2015%20City%20Place%20simultaneously.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2270c57a95-0968-4007-a21d-96efb55c9ff3%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20tale%20of%20two%20office%20markets%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20yawning%20gap%20between%20the%20health%20of%20top%20tier%20office%20space%20and%20the%20wider%20market%2C%20according%20to%20data%20from%20CBRE.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm%20labels%20new%20and%20heavily%20renovated%20spaces%20that%20meet%20a%20host%20of%20quality%20measures%20as%20%26quot%3Bprime%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%93%20a%20segment%20that%20encompasses%20only%208%25%20of%20overall%20office%20inventory%20nationally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20net%20total%20of%2049.3%20million%20square%20feet%20of%20prime%20space%20was%20absorbed%20between%202020%20and%20the%20first%20quarter%20of%202024%2C%20according%20to%20CBRE.%20Around%20170.3%20million%20square%20feet%20of%20net%20vacancy%20accrued%20in%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20office%20market%20during%20that%20same%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%20office%20vacancy%20nationally%20was%2019.1%25%20in%20June%2C%20close%20to%20a%20record%20level.%20Prime%20vacancy%20was%2015.5%25%20and%20CBRE%20forecasts%20that%20figure%20will%20drop%20by%20almost%20half%2C%20to%208.2%25%20by%202027%2C%20its%20pre-pandemic%20average.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20that%20this%20absorption%20estimate%20is%20conservative%2C%20and%20the%20prime%20vacancy%20rate%20could%20return%20to%20its%20pre-pandemic%20level%20sooner%20given%20continued%20job%20growth%2C%26quot%3B%20Jessica%20Morin%2C%20CBRE's%20director%20of%20US%20office%20research%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20top-of-the-market%20spaces%2C%20which%20charged%20a%2060%25%20premium%20before%20the%20pandemic%2C%20are%20now%2084%25%20more%20expensive%20than%20competing%20spaces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20little%20supply%2C%20that%20differential%20could%20grow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B8.2%25%20is%20a%20healthy%20prime%20market%20and%20we%20expect%20rent%20growth%20in%20this%20tranche%2C%26quot%3B%20Morin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDriving%20the%20solid%20metrics%20is%20a%20lack%20of%20new%20supply.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20a%20total%20of%2044%20million%20square%20feet%20of%20office%20space%20is%20presently%20under%20construction%2C%20only%20about%2017.3%20million%20square%20feet%20of%20it%2C%2039%25%20of%20the%20total%2C%20is%20considered%20prime%2C%20according%20to%20CBRE.%208%20million%20square%20feet%20of%20that%20is%20pre-leased%2C%20meaning%20that%20there%20is%20only%20about%2010%20million%20square%20feet%20of%20upcoming%20available%20top%20quality%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ccbe14d6-6f15-40b7-b453-f934e9df0594%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFinancing%20remains%20a%20sticking%20point%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20with%20the%20tailwinds%2C%20financing%20high%20end%20office%20construction%20remains%20a%20challenge.%20Banks%20have%20grown%20wary%20of%20lending%20to%20office%20projects%2C%20even%20those%20that%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20a%20financial%20success%2C%20because%20of%20broader%20concerns%20around%20declining%20values%2C%20increased%20foreclosures%2C%20and%20pote