K%2C%20I%20took%20up%20swimming.%20I%20loved%20it%20for%20a%20while%2C%20but%20when%20the%20winter%20mornings%20became%20too%20cold%20and%20dark%2C%20I%20quit.%20I%20tried%20dance%2C%20but%20because%20it%20involved%20getting%20on%20a%20bus%20on%20my%20own%20as%20a%2010-year-old%2C%20I%20quit%20that%20too.%20I'd%20done%20so%20many%20things%20that%20lasted%20a%20short%20period%20of%20time%2C%20so%20quitting%20things%20seemed%20normal%20to%20me%20and%20my%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20a%20parent%20now%2C%20and%20my%20daughters%20dance.%20Seeing%20them%20progress%20and%20how%20far%20I%20could%20have%20gone%20makes%20me%20regret%20my%20choice.%20But%20I've%20since%20learned%20the%20value%20of%20seeing%20things%20through.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fonly-child-had-multiple-under-3-years-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHaving%20children%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20a%20project%20for%20life%2C%20played%20a%20big%20role%20in%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229ec0c78b-d678-4b67-b8fb-c5a882ba2559%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20advice%20to%20expat%20parents%20is%20to%20help%20your%20kids%20keep%20up%20long-term%20friendships%20and%20hobbies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20of%20my%20upbringing%2C%20I'm%20a%20confident%20traveler.%20When%20I%20was%2026%2C%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamily-moved-from-uk-to-france-have-no-regrets-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emoved%20to%20France%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20three%20years.%20I've%20also%20taken%20my%20children%20on%20trips%20to%20see%20the%20world.%20We've%20been%20to%20India%20and%20France%20and%20have%20done%20road%20trips%20over%20the%20summers.%20But%20we%20always%20return%20to%20our%20home%20in%20Devon%2C%20England%2C%20where%20I%20work%20as%20a%20freelance%20writer%20and%20editor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20rooted%20and%20having%20a%20place%20to%20call%20home%20has%20been%20very%20important%20to%20me%20as%20an%20adult.%20I%20don't%20have%20some%20unquenched%20need%20to%20satisfy%2C%20perhaps%20because%20I've%20traveled%20a%20lot%20already.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20traveled%20to%20India%2C%20I%20met%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffinland-happiest-country-in-the-world-immigrants-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexpat%20couples%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20decided%20to%20live%20there%20full-time.%20They%20set%20up%20businesses%20there%2C%20and%20during%20monsoon%20seasons%2C%20they'd%20travel%20to%20other%20locations.%20The%20idea%20of%20doing%20that%20with%20children%20terrified%20me.%20Because%20of%20my%20childhood%20experiences%2C%20I%20couldn't%20bear%20to%20travel%20several%20times%20a%20year%20while%20maintaining%20an%20education%20and%20social%20life%20for%20my%20kids.%20I%20wanted%20them%20to%20have%20stable%20friend%20circles%20and%20activities%20they%20could%20keep%20doing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-moved-back-to-india-after-living-abroad-for-decade-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELiving%20abroad%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20wonderful%20thing%20to%20do%2C%20but%20one%20piece%20of%20advice%20I%20have%20for%20parents%20is%20to%20try%20to%20help%20their%20kids%20keep%20up%20friendships%20they've%20made%20through%20writing%20or%20meeting%20up%20later%20in%20life.%20And%20if%20you're%20moving%20between%20different%20places%2C%20make%20arrangements%20for%20your%20child%20to%20continue%20doing%20activities%20they%20love.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20upbringing%20made%20me%20self-reliant%2C%20which%20can%20be%20a%20valuable%20trait%2C%20but%20a%20negative%20impact%20is%20I've%20become%20someone%20who%20dips%20in%20and%20out%20of%20friendships%20and%20communities.%20I'm%20not%20a%20rotten%20friend%2C%20but%20I%20struggle%20to%20be%20consistent%20and%20value%20community%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstilling%20a%20sense%20of%20longevity%20into%20your%20kids'%20lives%20is%20a%20valuable%20thing%20to%20do.%20I%20didn't%20have%20that%2C%20but%20I%20would%20have%20benefited%20from%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%20personal%20travel%20or%20relocation%20story%20you%20want%20to%20share%20with%20Business%20Insider%3F%20Email%20ccheong%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftraveling-with-children-advice-expat-parents-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727952935000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66fe5a7a7de5c8fd4834e46c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftraveling-with-children-advice-expat-parents-2024-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sally%20Prag%2C%20who%20spent%20her%20childhood%20moving%20between%20countries%20for%20her%20father's%20job%2C%20shared%20advice%20for%20expat%20parents%20about%20raising%20kids%20abroad.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ccheong%40insider.com%20(Charissa%20Cheong)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftraveling-with-children-advice-expat-parents-2024-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Fire%20erupts%20on%20Ryanair%20flight%20before%20takeoff%20in%20Italy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727952913000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113906836%2Cimgsize-978350.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Ffire-erupts-on-ryanair-flight-before-takeoff-in-italy-around-200-passengers-safely-evacuated%2Farticleshow%2F113906873.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Ryanair%20flight%20at%20Brindisi%20airport%20in%20Italy%20faced%20a%20fire%20incident%20prior%20to%20takeoff%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20evacuation%20of%20184%20passengers.%20Firefighters%20intervened%2C%20and%20the%20airport%20was%20temporarily%20closed.%20Ryanair%20plans%20to%20use%20a%20spare%20aircraft%20to%20transport%20affected%20passengers%20to%20Turin%20later%20on%20Thursday.%20Operations%20at%20the%20airport%20have%20resumed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20WORLD%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22America%20is%20getting%20hammered%20on%20the%20'healthy'%20alternative%20to%20beer%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Photo%20collage%20of%20Man%20drinking%20from%20two%20canned%20cocktails%20with%20mini%20umbrellas%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66fd96fe7de5c8fd4834c1e7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3B%20Alyssa%20Powell%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDrinking%20non-beer%20alcohol%20out%20of%20a%20can%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%20the%20healthier%20alternative.%20Hard%20seltzers%2C%20spiked%20seltzers%2C%20and%20their%20ilk%20have%20been%20marketed%20as%20lighter%20than%20traditional%20alcoholic%20beverages.%20Their%20alcohol%20content%20is%20beer-ish%2C%20but%20the%20impact%20on%20your%20waistline%20isn't.%20To%20the%20extent%20that%20drinking%20alcohol%20is%20healthy%2C%20which%20it%20isn't%2C%20and%20assuming%20you're%20not%20a%20frat%20boy%20downing%2012%20White%20Claws%20in%2090%20minutes%2C%20the%20new%20category%20was%20meant%20to%20fill%20the%20slightly-better-for-you%20niche.%20Maybe%20the%20initial%20marketing%20was%20a%20little%20female-focused%2C%20but%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20guys%20came%20around.%20A%20sparkly%20little%20grapefruit-flavored%20malt%20beverage%20at%20the%20beach%20is%20a%20delight%20across%20the%20gender%20spectrum.%20Plus%2C%20who%20doesn't%20love%20to%20skip%20a%20bit%20of%20that%20beer-induced%20bloat%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20these%20prepackaged%20on-the-go%20drinks%20have%20evolved%2C%20and%20in%20many%20cases%20they've%20become%20much%20boozier.%20People%20aren't%20just%20picking%20up%205%25%20ABV%20hard%20seltzers%20on%20the%20way%20to%20the%20park%3B%20they're%20grabbing%20prepackaged%20gin%20and%20tonics%20and%20negronis%20and%20margaritas%20that%20have%20much%20more%20of%20a%20kick%20to%20them.%20The%20hard%20seltzers%20now%20come%20in%20supercharged%20varieties%2C%20too.%20Brands%20living%20on%20the%20same%20shelf%20can%20have%20a%20wide%20variety%20of%20effects%3A%20Nutrl%20Spirits%20will%20hit%20you%20like%20a%20regular%20seltzer%2C%20while%20Cutwater%20will%20screw%20you%20up.%20Both%20are%20owned%20by%20Budweiser's%20parent%20company%2C%20Anheuser-Busch%20InBev%2C%20which%20has%20reported%20double-digit%20growth%20in%20volume%20for%20its%20spirits-based%20portfolio%20this%20year.%20The%20next%20time%20you%20grab%20a%20drink%20in%20a%20can%2C%20you%20might%20want%20to%20take%20a%20second%20look%20at%20the%20ABV%20%E2%80%94%20or%20be%20prepared%20to%20wind%20up%20under%20the%20table.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EReady-to-drink%20alcoholic%20beverages%20%E2%80%94%20industry%20speak%20for%20canned%20and%20bottled%20non-beer%20drinks%20%E2%80%94%20have%20been%20around%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20Smirnoff%20Ice%2C%20Mike's%20Hard%20Lemonade%2C%20and%20Twisted%20Tea%20were%20introduced%20around%20the%20turn%20of%20the%20century.%20In%20the%202010s%2C%20the%20hard%20seltzers%20started%20to%20pop%20up%2C%20with%20names%20like%20White%20Claw%20and%20Truly%2C%20both%20of%20which%20launched%20in%202016.%20Their%20ABV%20was%20typically%20similar%20to%20the%20average%20beer%2C%20somewhere%20between%204%25%20and%206%25.%20The%20pandemic%20supercharged%20the%20trend%3A%20The%20bars%20closed%2C%20and%20people%20were%20left%20to%20their%20own%20devices%2C%20alcohol-wise%20%E2%80%94%20and%20they%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fexperts-say-coronavirus-may-cause-spike-in-alcohol-abuse-2020-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edrinking%20more%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20the%20pandemic%2C%20hard%20seltzers%20really%20blew%20up%2C%20and%20I%20think%20hard%20seltzers%20are%20one%20of%20those%20ones%20that%20were%20perceived%20as%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20a%20better-for-you%20option%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Kaleigh%20Theriault%2C%20an%20associate%20director%20of%20beverage-alcohol%20thought%20leadership%20at%20NIQ%2C%20a%20market%20research%20firm.%20Unfortunately%2C%20there's%20no%20kind%20of%20alcohol%20that's%20%3Cem%3Eactually%3C%2Fem%3E%20better%20for%20you%2C%20but%20the%20companies%20leaned%20in%20%E2%80%94%20many%20of%20the%20drinks%20were%20positioned%20as%20low-calorie%2C%20low-carb%2C%20low-sugar%2C%20etc.%2C%20and%20many%20still%20are.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENIQ%20dubbed%202020%20the%20%26quot%3Bsummer%20of%20seltzers.%26quot%3B%20Recognizing%20the%20drinks'%20popularity%2C%20a%20bunch%20of%20companies%20threw%20their%20hat%20in%20the%20ring%2C%20including%20AB%20InBev%20and%20Coca-Cola.%20The%20market%20got%20saturated%2C%20and%20people%20started%20to%20realize%20there%20could%20be%20a%20lot%20more%20to%20canned%20alcohol%20than%20beer%20and%20hard%20seltzers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20so%20many%20more%20products%20available%20that%20another%20lime%20hard%20seltzer%20probably%20isn't%20going%20to%20get%20much%20shelf%20space%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Chris%20Budzik%2C%20a%20senior%20market%20analyst%20at%20IWSR%2C%20which%20covers%20the%20alcoholic-beverage%20industry.%20%26quot%3BSo%20companies%20are%20having%20to%20innovate%20more%20and%20more%2C%20and%20that%20has%20led%20to%20some%20higher-ABV%20canned%20cocktails.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20NIQ%2C%20%26quot%3Bfourth%20category%26quot%3B%20sales%20%E2%80%94%20meaning%20ready-to-drink%20and%20ready-to-serve%20alcoholic%20beverages%20%E2%80%94%20have%20reached%20%2413.1%20billion%20in%20sales%20over%20the%20past%20year%2C%20up%20from%20%2412.6%20billion%20in%20the%20year%20before%20and%20%2411.8%20billion%20two%20years%20ago.%20It%20now%20represents%2012%25%20of%20total%20alcohol%20sales%20in%20dollars.%20Hard-seltzer%20sales%20are%20at%20%243.7%20billion%2C%20but%20they've%20declined%20by%2013.1%25%20over%20the%20past%20year%20as%20they've%20come%20back%20down%20to%20a%20post-pandemic%20earth.%20Meanwhile%2C%20spirits-based%20drinks%20are%20up%20by%2022.5%25%2C%20to%20%242.5%20billion.%20(Flavored%20malt%20beverages%2C%20such%20as%20Cayman%20Jack%2C%20are%20up%20too%2C%20by%209.9%25%2C%20to%20%245.4%20billion.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20lot%20of%20these%20spirits-based%20drinks%20have%20a%20higher%20ABV%2C%20in%20part%20because%20they%20have%20to%20%E2%80%94%20there's%20just%20no%20way%20to%20make%20a%20low-alcohol%20Manhattan.%20You%20add%20vodka%20or%20gin%20or%20tequila%20to%20the%20mix%2C%20and%20the%20alcohol%20content%20goes%20up.%20And%20as%20consumers%20have%20been%20introduced%20to%20the%20idea%20of%20drinks%20in%20a%20can%2C%20they've%20expanded%20their%20horizons.%20If%20I%20can%20have%20a%20mediocre%20hard%20seltzer%20on%20the%20go%2C%20why%20not%20up%20my%20game%20and%20get%20a%20nice%20crisp%20G%26amp%3BT%3F%20The%20authenticity%20of%20the%20spirit%20in%20the%20drink%20is%20appealing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKate%20Bernot%2C%20the%20lead%20analyst%20at%20Sightlines%2C%20an%20analyst%20group%20that%20covers%20the%20alcohol%20industry%2C%20said%20there%20were%20three%20main%20factors%20in%20the%20growth%20of%20the%20RTD%20cocktail%20sector%20and%20the%20accompanying%20increased%20booziness%3A%20consumer%20taste%2C%20corporate%20ambition%2C%20and%20state%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20are%20jazzed%20about%20the%20idea%20of%20getting%20something%20prepackaged%20(and%20cheaper)%20at%20a%20store.%20It's%20expensive%20and%20annoying%20to%20buy%20all%20the%20ingredients%20you%20need%20to%20concoct%20an%20espresso%20martini%20or%20a%20mai%20tai%20at%20home%2C%20and%20sometimes%20you%20just%20don't%20want%20to%20go%20to%20a%20bar.%20You%20might%20as%20well%20just%20grab%20a%20Cutwater.%20The%20portability%20is%20also%20a%20big%20draw%3A%20You%20can%20bring%20a%20few%20cans%20to%20the%20beach%20with%20you%2C%20or%20grab%20a%20six-pack%20on%20the%20way%20to%20a%20dinner%20as%20a%20substitute%20for%20the%20bottle%20of%20wine%20you%20might%20normally%20give%20the%20host.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20genuine%20consumer%20organic%20excitement%2C%26quot%3B%20Bernot%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20fast-rising%20popularity%20of%20RTD%20alcoholic%20beverages%2C%20there%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20new%20brands%20%E2%80%94%20many%20have%20been%20on%20the%20shelf%20for%20less%20than%20a%20year.%20The%20next%20time%20you%20go%20to%20the%20liquor%20store%20or%20wherever%20it%20is%20in%20your%20area%20that's%20allowed%20to%20sell%20alcohol%2C%20take%20a%20look%20at%20all%20the%20options%20%E2%80%94%20there%20are%20probably%20a%20lot%20of%20names%20you've%20never%20even%20heard%20of.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20just%20so%20many%20more%20options%20nowadays%2C%26quot%3B%20Theriault%2C%20from%20NIQ%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20also%20overwhelming.%20%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVarious%20states%20have%20passed%20laws%20to%20allow%20distilled-spirits%20products%20like%20canned%20cocktails%20to%20be%20sold%20in%20places%20where%20they%20previously%20couldn't%20be%20or%20have%20changed%20the%20structure%20of%20how%20such%20beverages%20are%20taxed.%20Pennsylvania%20changed%20its%20laws%20to%20let%20grocery%20stores%20and%20convenience%20stores%20sell%20canned%20cocktails%20of%20up%20to%2012.5%25%20ABV%20starting%20in%20September.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.freep.com%2Fstory%2Fnews%2Flocal%2Fmichigan%2F2021%2F05%2F24%2Fmichigan-canned-cocktail-laws%2F7419661002%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMichigan%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthehill.com%2Fhomenews%2Fstate-watch%2F3515777-vermont-lowers-ready-to-drink-spirits-taxes%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVermont%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20lowered%20RTD%20taxes.%20Bernot%20described%20the%20changes%20as%20a%20result%20of%20%26quot%3Ba%20combination%20of%20consumer%20demand%2C%20more%20brands%2C%20and%20more%20retail%20access.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20kind%20of%20impossible%20not%20to%20notice%20the%20proliferation%20of%20canned%20cocktails%20%E2%80%94%20which%20are%20increasingly%20available%20at%20sporting%20events%20and%20concerts%20and%20even%20at%20bars%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20in%20a%20moment%20when%20the%20service%20sector%20is%20struggling%20to%20find%20workers.%20They're%20now%20common%20in%20social%20settings%3B%20buying%20a%20six-pack%20of%20canned%20margaritas%20isn't%20that%20different%20from%20picking%20up%20a%20six-pack%20of%20beers.%20But%20they%20also%20come%20with%20some%20risks%20for%20those%20not%20in%20the%20know.%20A%20friend%20and%20I%20regularly%20go%20on%20walks%20with%20her%20dog%20in%20my%20neighborhood%2C%20accompanied%20by%20a%20couple%20of%20cans%20of%20gin%20and%20tonic.%20The%20other%20day%20I%20pointed%20out%20to%20her%20that%20the%20ABV%20on%20those%20little%20cans%20was%20three%20times%20a%20Bud%20Light%20%E2%80%94%20she%20had%20no%20idea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20surprise%20booziness%20of%20some%20of%20the%20canned%20cocktails%20has%20become%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20meme.%20Someone%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Ftylathecreative%2Fstatus%2F1832996136824566176%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecently%20posted%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20picture%20of%20a%20Cutwater%20lemon-drop%20martini%20accompanied%20by%20the%20caption%20%26quot%3BI%20just%20drank%20two%20of%20these%20and%20now%20I'm%20responding%20to%20everyone's%20Instagram%20story%20like%20they%20sent%20it%20to%20me%20personally.%26quot%3B%20Probably%20because%20those%20puppies%20are%2011%25%20ABV.%20People%20who%20are%20choosing%20spirits%20over%20beer%20more%20often%20are%20consuming%20a%20lot%20more%20alcohol%20per%20drink%20than%20they%20used%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20just%20the%20canned%20cocktails%20that%20are%20getting%20drunker%2C%20either.%20White%20Claw%20and%20Truly%20now%20make%20extra-alcoholic%20varieties.%20Canned%20wines%20can%20be%20pretty%20dangerous%2C%20because%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20don't%20realize%20that%20they%20often%20actually%20have%20two%20glasses%2C%20not%20one.%20And%20last%20year%2C%20Modelo%20surpassed%20Bud%20Light%20as%20the%20most%20popular%20beer%20in%20America%3B%20its%20ABV%20is%20slightly%20higher.%20IPAs%20with%20high%20alcohol%20content%20have%20proliferated.%20One%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fvinepair.com%2Fbooze-news%2Fvoodoo-ranger-ipa-collection-sales%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DSo%2520Is%2520the%2520Second.%2C-words%253A%2520Olivia%2520White%26amp%3Btext%3DVoodoo%2520Ranger%2520Imperial%2520IPA%2520is%2Cto%2520new%2520data%2520from%2520Brewbound.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emost%20popular%20craft%20beers%20in%20the%20country%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20Voodoo%20Ranger%20Imperial%20IPA%2C%20which%20is%209%25%20ABV%20and%20also%20comes%20in%20a%2019.2-ounce%20can%2C%20if%20that's%20something%20you're%20into.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20a%20time%20to%20be%20alive%2C%26quot%3B%20Bernot%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20just%20a%20lot%20of%20beer%2C%20man.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBudzik%20said%20he'd%20%26quot%3Bpersonally%20noticed%20that%20the%208%25%20double%20IPAs%20have%20become%20the%20standard.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbeverage-analysts-predict-non-alcoholic-spirits-to-grow-in-2022-2021-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENonalcoholic%20beverages%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20like%20zero-proof%20beers%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsober-bars-booming-across-country-alcohol-free-lifestyle-dry-january-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emocktails%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20are%20growing%2C%20too%2C%20which%20has%20led%20to%20almost%20a%20hollowing%20out%20of%20the%20middle%20on%20alcohol.%20Either%20people%20are%20getting%20really%20drunk%20or%20they're%20not%20drinking.%20At%20this%20point%2C%20a%20run-of-the-mill%20lager%20or%20seltzer%20is%20basically%20considered%20a%20light%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrends%20are%20constantly%20coming%20and%20going%2C%20including%20in%20alcohol.%20In%20such%20a%20crowded%20industry%2C%20there's%20no%20guarantee%20all%20these%20brands%20and%20drinks%20will%20stick%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20something%20becomes%20popular%2C%20it's%20going%20to%20get%20some%20play.%20Products%20are%20going%20to%20come%20out%20that%20reflect%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Budzik%20said.%20%26quot%3BWill%20they%20still%20be%20here%20in%20five%20years%3F%20Who%20knows.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20I%20guess%20if%20there's%20a%20canned%20cocktail%20you're%20really%20into%2C%20maybe%20stock%20up.%20Or%20get%20ready%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20do%20some%20mixology%20on%20your%20own.%20And%20in%20the%20meantime%2C%20really%2C%20check%20the%20ABV%20on%20the%20label%20before%20you're%20in%20for%20an%20unintended%20wild%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Femily-stewart%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EEmily%20Stewart%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20correspondent%20at%20Business%20Insider%2C%20writing%20about%20business%20and%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhard-seltzer-canned-cocktail-high-abv-beer-alcohol-drinks-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727952782000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66fd97279e0c5c2eeeea202e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhard-seltzer-canned-cocktail-high-abv-beer-alcohol-drinks-2024-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Alcohol%20in%20a%20can%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%20a%20healthier%2C%20lighter%20alternative%20to%20beer.%20Nowadays%2C%20it's%20just%20getting%20Amer