%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66fac1c0f44bdb4cfa3819e5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwoman-lost-159-pounds-how-diet-changed-before-after-2024-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Maria%20Kirkeland%20made%20changes%20to%20her%20diet%20slowly%2C%20such%20as%20gradually%20swapping%20fries%20for%20potatoes%20(but%20not%20always).%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22rhosie%40businessinsider.com%20(Rachel%20Hosie)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwoman-lost-159-pounds-how-diet-changed-before-after-2024-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Dating%20apps%20helped%20me%20find%20love.%20Now%20they've%20turned%20into%20a%20total%20scam.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Statue%20with%20a%20giant%20heart.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66fc3e7a7518aa57bc9fc7c0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ENicolas%20Ortega%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfew%20weeks%20after%20a%20recent%20breakup%2C%20I%20hesitantly%20opened%20up%20the%20App%20Store%20and%20started%20the%20renewal%20ritual%20of%20modern%20dating%3A%20reinstalling%20the%20apps.%20This%20was%20once%20exciting%2C%20the%20start%20of%20an%20adventure.%20But%20this%20time%2C%20seeing%20progress%20bars%20slowly%20load%2C%20I%20was%20filled%20with%20dread.%20I%20knew%20I%20wanted%20to%20date%20again%20%E2%80%94%20just%20on%20a%20version%20of%20the%20apps%20that%20no%20longer%20existed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELately%2C%20nearly%20every%20conversation%20with%20single%20friends%20and%20strangers%20and%20those%20in%20open%20relationships%20descends%20into%20collective%20mourning%20about%20the%20abysmal%20state%20of%20the%20apps.%20When%20I'm%20out%20at%20dinner%2C%20getting%20my%20hair%20cut%2C%20or%20even%20taping%20a%20recent%20podcast%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Efor%20work%2C%20the%20same%20complaints%20come%20back%3A%20They're%20expensive%2C%20exhausting%2C%20manipulative%2C%20and%20overrun%20with%20scams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20feel%20betrayed.%20I've%20been%20on%20dating%20sites%20and%20apps%20for%20the%20past%2017%20years.%20Online%20dating%20not%20only%20allowed%20me%20to%20meet%20some%20of%20the%20most%20important%20people%20in%20my%20life%20but%20also%20let%20me%20learn%20that%20I%20could%20truly%20find%20love%2C%20something%20I%20long%20doubted%20was%20possible.%20When%20they%20first%20worked%2C%20they%20made%20it%20effortless%2C%20even%20thrilling%2C%20to%20find%20people%20I%20thought%20I'd%20never%20be%20able%20to%20find.%20Now%2C%20trudging%20through%20the%20apps%20feels%20draining.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnline%20dating%20always%20had%20its%20toxic%20side%2C%20especially%20for%20women%20dating%20men.%20When%20I%20share%20dating%20horror%20stories%20with%20my%20female%20friends%2C%20as%20a%20straight%20guy%2C%20there's%20no%20comparison.%20Even%20on%20my%20worst%20day%20%E2%80%94%20like%20the%20night%20I%20ended%20up%20in%20a%20not-so-romantic%20Uber%20with%20a%20white%20supremacist%20whose%20comments%20were%20so%20appalling%20I%20left%20a%20200%25%20tip%20for%20the%20driver%20forced%20to%20overhear%20them%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20never%20as%20bad%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pewresearch.org%2Finternet%2F2023%2F02%2F02%2Ffrom-looking-for-love-to-swiping-the-field-online-dating-in-the-u-s%2Fpi_2023-02-02_online-dating_0-06-png%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ethe%20abuse%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20women%20routinely%20face.%20Still%2C%20as%20fortunate%20as%20I%20feel%20with%20most%20aspects%20of%20dating%2C%20the%20apps%20I%20and%20tens%20of%20millions%20of%20us%20rely%20on%20to%20find%20dates%20increasingly%20leave%20me%20feeling%20invisible%2C%20exploited%2C%20and%20ripped%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20first%20stumbled%20onto%20the%20dating%20white%20pages%20that%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FMatch.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMatch.com%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202007%2C%20I%20had%20spent%20most%20of%20my%20life%20feeling%20undateable.%20I%20felt%20awkward%2C%20overly%20cerebral%2C%20offtrack%2C%20underperforming%2C%20out%20of%20shape%20%E2%80%94%20entirely%20undesirable.%20I%20didn't%20date%20in%20high%20school%2C%20and%20my%20one%20try%20in%20college%20ended%20in%20disaster.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20I%20was%2023%2C%20a%20nerdy%20meet-cute%20changed%20my%20thinking.%20It%20was%20my%20first%20summer%20in%20DC%2C%20when%20I%20was%20trying%20and%20failing%20to%20live%20out%20some%20sort%20of%20%26quot%3BWest%20Wing%26quot%3B%20fantasy%20of%20working%20in%20politics.%20That%20June%2C%20I%20found%20myself%20at%20that%20annual%20festival%20of%20Beltway%20wonkery%2C%20the%20Congressional%20Baseball%20Game.%20An%20overheard%20comment%20about%20constitutional%20law%20led%20to%20a%20conversation%20with%20a%20congressional%20intern%20in%20front%20of%20me.%20It%20was%20love%20at%20First%20Amendment.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2019%2F04%2F10%2Fcrosswords%2Ffrom-generation-to-generation-essay.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EWhat%20followed%20was%20a%20summer%20of%20word%20games%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Washington%20adventures%2C%20and%20clumsily%20learning%20how%20to%20date.%20Our%20relationship%20was%20wonderful%2C%20but%20it%20didn't%20outlive%20the%20internship.%20This%20brief%20romance%2C%20however%2C%20taught%20me%20that%2C%20as%20unlikely%20as%20it%20felt%2C%20there%20were%20people%20interested%20in%20dating%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20where%20to%20find%20them%3F%20I%20was%20too%20shy%20to%20ever%20ask%20out%20strangers%20at%20a%20bar%2C%20my%20self-esteem%20was%20too%20low%20to%20think%20colleagues%20or%20friends%20were%20interested%2C%20and%20I%20was%20terrified%20that%20I'd%20make%20an%20unwanted%20advance%20in%20a%20social%20setting%2C%20at%20work%2C%20or%20at%20school%20that%20would%20make%20someone%20feel%20uncomfortable%20around%20me%20forever.%20Online%20dating%20gave%20me%20the%20clarity%20to%20feel%20comfortable%20finally%20asking%20women%20out%2C%20a%20meeting%20place%20where%20there%20was%20no%20ambiguity%20about%20what%20we%20sought.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20I%20wasn't%20alone%20in%20craving%20that%20clarity%2C%20even%20if%20dating%20platforms%20still%20had%20a%20patina%20of%20ick.%20A%202003%20New%20York%20Times%20headline%20read%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2003%2F06%2F29%2Fus%2Fonline-dating-sheds-its-stigma-as-loserscom.html%3FsearchResultPosition%3D1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EOnline%20Dating%20Sheds%20Its%20Stigma%20as%20%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FLosers.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ELosers.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20before%20damning%20internet%20romantics%20with%20dim%20praise%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BOnline%20dating%2C%20once%20viewed%20as%20a%20refuge%20for%20the%20socially%20inept%20and%20as%20a%20faintly%20disrespectable%20way%20to%20meet%20other%20people%2C%20is%20rapidly%20becoming%20a%20fixture%20of%20single%20life.%26quot%3B%20By%202007%2C%20Match%20had%20more%20than%2042%20million%20users.%20Out%20of%20countless%20dating%20sites%2C%20Match%20was%20the%20only%20one%20with%20the%20scale%20to%20run%20TV%20ads%20with%20celebrities%20like%20Dr.%20Phil%20(which%2C%20shockingly%2C%20wasn't%20a%20red%20flag%20at%20the%20time).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELogging%20in%20to%20mid-aughts-era%20Match%2C%20I%20saw%20a%20world%20of%20pixelated%20possibilities%2C%20so%20many%20women%20so%20close%20by.%20It%20was%20electrifying%2C%20and%20I%20felt%20my%20mind%20mired%20in%20infinite%20possibilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20turned%20to%20the%20filters%2C%20crudely%20defining%20who%20met%20my%20criteria%2C%20and%20who%20didn't.%20And%20I%20saw%20how%20wildly%20those%20criteria%20shifted%20with%20how%20I%20felt%20about%20myself.%20On%20days%20I%20brimmed%20with%20self-confidence%2C%20say%20after%20a%20win%20at%20work%2C%20I%20messaged%20the%20women%20who%20excited%20me%20most.%20I%20still%20messaged%20them%20expecting%20rejection%20but%20hoping%20rejection%20from%20afar%20would%20hurt%20less.%20More%20often%2C%20I%20filtered%20them%20out%2C%20caving%20to%20the%20doubt%20they%20were%20too%20good%20to%20settle%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFiltering%20was%20frustrating.%20As%20I%20looked%20for%20matches%2C%20the%20list%20seemed%20both%20too%20broad%20and%20too%20narrow.%20Take%20religion.%20I%20didn't%20care%20which%20faith%20they%20listed.%20What%20I%20cared%20about%20was%20their%20empathy%20and%20openness%20to%20my%20own%20strange%20mix%20of%20secularism%2C%20Judaism%2C%20and%20ambivalent%20agnosticism.%20But%20there's%20no%20checkbox%20for%20curiosity%20and%20kindness.%20Often%2C%20what%20mattered%20most%20to%20me%20(intellect%2C%20humor%2C%20and%20nerdiness)%20fell%20outside%20Match's%20categories.%20Still%2C%20I%20begrudgingly%20accepted%20the%20crude%20factors%20that%20did%20matter%20to%20me%20(education%20level%2C%20proximity%2C%20and%20body%20type)%2C%20and%20I%20dove%20into%20the%20novellas%20that%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FMatch.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMatch.com%3C%2Fa%3E%20dating%20profiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20incredible%20just%20how%20much%20we%20all%20wrote.%20Beyond%20the%20basics%20%E2%80%94%20relationship%20status%2C%20politics%2C%20education%2C%20smoking%2C%20and%20drinking%20%E2%80%94%20profiles%20detailed%20everything%20from%20income%20to%20preferred%20industries.%20And%20that%20was%20before%20the%20lengthy%20biographical%20essays.%20I%20look%20back%20at%20my%20own%20bio%20in%20horror.%20Perhaps%20it's%20my%20failed%20nonchalance%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20enjoy%20traveling%2C%20but%20my%20trips%20have%20generally%20been%20confined%20to%20Western%20Europe.%20I%20want%20to%20explore%20the%20Middle%20East%20and%20Asia%20in%20the%20coming%20years.%26quot%3B%20Or%20my%20not-so-suave%20show%20of%20culture%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20play%20guitar%20and%20a%20couple%20other%20instruments%2C%20and%20I'm%20trying%20to%20figure%20out%20the%20DC%20art%20scene.%26quot%3B%20I%20tried%20so%20hard%20to%20show%20I%20was%20interesting%20that%20I%20never%20thought%20about%20how%20off-putting%20my%20pretension%20was.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20early%20online%20matchmaking%20flooded%20users%20with%20possibilities%20and%20gave%20us%20the%20tools%20to%20at%20least%20try%20to%20make%20sense%20of%20it.%20And%20in%20many%20ways%2C%20for%20a%20young%2C%20awkward%20nerd%20like%20me%2C%20it%20was%20perfect.%20How%20I%20handled%20the%20dates%20themselves%2C%20less%20so.%20My%20early%20efforts%20fit%20what%20I%20called%20%26quot%3Bthe%20rule%20of%20threes%26quot%3B%3A%20Three%20messages%20averaged%20one%20response%2C%20three%20responses%20averaged%20one%20date%2C%20three%20dates%20averaged%20one%20second%20date%2C%20and%20three%20second%20dates%20averaged%20a%20third.%20It%20wasn't%20an%20exact%20pattern%2C%20but%20in%20my%20three%20years%20of%20DC%20dating%2C%20I%20had%20only%20one%20third%20date.%20She%20politely%20declined%20a%20fourth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20early%20dates%20were%20as%20awkward%20as%20they%20were%20indispensable.%20Even%20as%20I%20felt%20stuck%20professionally%20and%20doubted%20I%20could%20ever%20reach%20the%20future%20I%20wanted%2C%20I%20found%20the%20reservoir%20of%20confidence%20to%20comfortably%20talk%20to%20strangers.%20I%20learned%20a%20whole%20set%20of%20social%20skills%20that%20it%20felt%20like%20other%20people%20just%20magically%20knew.%20Still%2C%20the%20sting%20of%20serial%20rejection%20took%20its%20toll%2C%20telling%20me%20that%20my%20self-hatred%20and%20despair%20were%20right%20all%20along.%20When%20friends%20tried%20to%20cheer%20me%20up%2C%20I'd%20respond%20that%20I%20had%20the%20dataset%20to%20prove%20them%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20left%20DC%20for%20law%20school%2C%20I%20abandoned%20online%20dating.%20The%20first%20year%2C%20it%20was%20for%20school%20itself.%20I%20started%20in%202010%2C%20at%20the%20nadir%20of%20the%20post-financial-crisis%20legal%20market%2C%20and%20I%20was%20terrified%20I'd%20end%20up%20unemployable.%20For%20the%20first%20time%20in%20my%20life%2C%20I%20took%20school%20seriously%2C%20and%20shut%20everything%20else%20out.%20With%20no%20shortage%20of%20luck%2C%20I%20aced%20my%20exams%20and%20even%20transferred%20to%20Harvard%20Law.%20After%20all%20those%20years%20adrift%20in%20DC%2C%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20back%20on%20track.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20second%20year%2C%20I%20stayed%20offline%20for%20a%20very%20different%20reason%3A%20I%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20one%20of%20my%20classmates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20tumultuous%20time.%20She%20was%20way%20smarter%20than%20me%2C%20indescribably%20cool%2C%20and%20somehow%20in%20love%20with%20me.%20But%20she%20was%20also%20unstable%2C%20unfaithful%2C%20and%20self-destructive.%20When%20I%20ended%20our%20relationship%20in%202012%2C%20she%20attempted%20suicide.%20After%20I%20rushed%20her%20unconscious%20body%20to%20the%20ER%2C%20I%20spent%20the%20first%20week%20of%20our%20breakup%20ferrying%20care%20packages%20to%20her%20locked%20hospital%20ward.%20(We%20hadn't%20spoken%20for%20a%20few%20years%20when%20I%20found%20out%20in%202020%20that%20she%20had%20taken%20her%20own%20life%2C%20leaving%20this%20world%20a%20deeply%20diminished%20place.%20The%20news%20gutted%20me.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20spent%20some%20time%20alone%20after%20things%20ended%2C%20but%20by%20the%20end%20of%202012%2C%20I%20was%20ready%20to%20re-embrace%20online%20dating.%20Partly%20it%20was%20my%20law-school%20success%20and%20fancy-schmancy%20job%20offer.%20Those%20pretentious%20labels%20let%20me%20see%20beneath%20the%20self-loathing%20and%20believe%20in%20the%20best%20of%20myself.%20But%20it%20was%20also%20the%20intense%20validation%20that%20a%20second%20person%20%E2%80%94%20against%20all%20my%20expectations%20%E2%80%94%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20me.%20I%20began%20to%20believe%20I%20could%20find%20more%20than%20fleeting%20connection%20on%20the%20apps.%20I%20actually%20hoped%20for%20love.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20dating%20world%20I%20was%20tiptoeing%20back%20into%20was%20not%20the%20same.%20Tinder%20had%20arrived%2C%20the%20swipe%20era%20had%20been%20born%2C%20and%20dating%20would%20never%20be%20the%20same.%20After%20years%20of%20stagnation%2C%20the%20dating-app%20market%20went%20into%20a%20frenzy%20of%20growth%2C%20and%20by%202013%2C%20online%20dating%20was%20the%20most%20common%20way%20for%20straight%20couples%20to%20meet.%20It%20wasn't%20just%20popular%3B%20it%20was%20cool.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECharlotte%20Fox%20Weber%2C%20a%20psychotherapist%20and%20the%20author%20of%20%26quot%3BTell%20Me%20What%20You%20Want%26quot%3B%20(and%2C%20full%20disclosure%2C%20my%20cousin)%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20past%20decade%20has%20transformed%20our%20attitudes%20towards%20online%20dating.%26quot%3B%20Weber%20added%20that%20her%20clients%20often%20%26quot%3Bcompare%20it%20to%20online%20shopping%20%E2%80%94%20no%20store%20hours%2C%20endless%20possibilities%2C%20a%20sense%20of%20potential.%26quot%3B%20She%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bthough%20the%20apps%20claim%20to%20promote%20transparency%2C%20this%20is%20often%20performative%2C%20driving%20deception%20that%20strains%20trust%20and%20undermines%20genuine%20connection.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20Tinder%2C%20my%20shift%20in%20dating%20psychology%20was%20almost%20immediate.%20Instead%20of%20laboring%20over%20lengthy%20replies%20to%20thoughtful%20profiles%2C%20I%20swiped%20on%20a%20whim.%20After%20the%20traumatic%20intensity%20of%20my%20relationship%2C%20it%20was%20a%20relief%20to%20connect%20with%20such%20low%20stakes.%20It%20started%20as%20a%20fun%20game%2C%20a%20parade%20of%20pings%20bombarding%20my%20brain%20with%20dopamine.%20Dating%20went%20from%20a%20deliberative%20and%20often%20taxing%20task%20to%20the%20background%20noise%20of%20my%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20early%20Tinder%20days%20were%20deeply%20imperfect.%20Appification%20meant%20even%20less%20intentionality%2C%20and%20constant%20interaction%20meant%20constant%20potential%20for%20disappointment.%20Still%2C%20Tinder%20made%20it%20just%20as%20easy%20to%20disconnect%20as%20it%20was%20to%20connect.%20Swiping%20became%20Tinder's%20brand%2C%20but%20leveraging%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftechcrunch.com%2F2013%2F01%2F03%2Ftinder-finding-traction-on-campuses-hatch-labs-new-dating-app-makes-it-easy-to-break-the-ice%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EFacebook%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20logins%20was%20just%20as%20important%20to%20its%20success.%20Connecting%20profiles%20to%20our%20existing%20digital%20lives%20dramatically%20eased%20fears%20about%20meeting%20a%20stranger%20online.%20Within%20a%20few%20years%2C%20my%20fellow%20millennials%20and%20I%20were%20reportedly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Flife-style%2Fdating-apps-millenials-10-hours-per-week-tinder-bumble-romance-love-a8174006.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Espending%2010%20hours%20a%20week%20on%20dating%20apps%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20for%20me%2C%20that%20time%20felt%20well%20spent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESure%2C%20not%20every%20date%20was%20life-changing%2C%20but%20I%20connected%20with%20some%20of%20the%20most%20incredible%20people%20I've%20known.%20On%20Match%2C%20I%20went%20on%20a%20date%20every%20week%20or%20two.%20On%20Tinder%2C%20every%20night%20or%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETinder%20and%20the%20other%20apps%20let%20me%20authentically%20navigate%20the%20dating%20world%20as%20my%20best%20self%2C%20and%20even%20find%20love.%20Occasionally%2C%20I%20would%20try%20to%20look%20at%20how%20unrecognizable%20my%20life%20had%20become%20from%20the%20awkward%20young%20man%20floundering%20and%20filtering%20profiles%20on%20his%20laptop%20with%20ever-fading%20hopes.%20Despite%20its%20dysfunction%2C%20despite%20its%20dangers%2C%20that%20was%20a%20gift%20online%20dating%20gave%20me%20and%20millions%20of%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20times%2C%20though%2C%20the%20breeziness%20of%20swiping%20let%20me%20be%20too%20thoughtless%20with%20my%20date's%20wants%20and%20needs.%20We%20all%20crave%20to%20be%20the%20hero%20of%20our%20own%20narrative%2C%20but%20I'm%20sure%20there%20are%20times%20when%20I've%20played%20villain%2C%20avoiding%20hard%20conversations%2C%20ignoring%20incompatibilities%2C%20and%20ending%20serious%20relationships%20all%20too%20abruptly.%20After%20I'd%20spent%20so%20many%20years%20craving%20affection%2C%20it%20was%20easy%20for%20me%20to%20front-load%20my%20vulnerability%2C%20to%20dive%20in%20heart-first%2C%20even%20when%20I%20doubted%20our%20long-term%20potential.%20I%20recreated%20the%20same%20failed%20cycle%20over%20and%20over%20again%3A%20falling%20too%20quickly%2C%20denying%20the%20problem%2C%20and%20running%20away%20more%20quickly%20still.%20The%20apps%20control%20so%20much%20of%20how%20we%20meet%20new%20people%2C%20but%20they%20don't%20control%20whether%20we%20let%20ourselves%20fall%20short%20with%20those%20we%20already%20know.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20app%20experience%20changed%2C%20the%20online%20dating%20industry%20remained%20surprisingly%20stagnant.%20When%20I%20switched%20to%20Tinder%2C%20I%20thought%20I%20was%20leaving%20Match%20behind%2C%20but%20the%20company%20was%20quietly%20orchestrating%20its%20merger-based%20metastasization%20into%20the%20matchmaking%20monopoly%20known%20today%20as%20the%20Match%20Group.%20This%20multi-billion%20dollar%20behemoth%20not%20only%20owns%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3Db7e22a8c4c56b6faba4e914331dc542586c0527c262df0a9c71fc55c486aa65e%26postID%3D66fc386de5b54083003ef8ab%26postSlug%3Ddating-apps-find-love-romance-online-tinder-match-total-scam-2024-10%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fmatch.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ematch.com%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Tinder%2C%20but%20OKCupid%2C%20Meetic%2C%20Hinge%2C%20Pairs%2C%20Plenty%20of%20Fish%2C%20BLK%2C%20The%20League%2C%20and%20a%20total%20of%20more%20than%2045%20dating%20brands.%20It%20feels%20like%20there%20are%20constantly%20more%20apps%2C%20but%20fewer%20choices%20and%20those%20choices%20are%20getting%20worse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Screen%20on%20an%20iPhone%20with%20dating%20apps%20shown.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658f4e2fab6f2ebb11f7eceb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIn%20one%20month%2C%20I%20often%20easily%20spend%20hundreds%20of%20dollars%20%E2%80%94%20not%20the%20cost%20of%20going%20on%20dates%2C%20not%20the%20cost%20of%20getting%20to%20know%20someone%20%E2%80%94%20but%20the%20cost%20of%20simply%20bribing%20the%20app%20to%20let%20me%20be%20seen.%3Cp%3EKoshiro%20K%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIronically%2C%20as%20the%20apps%20get%20more%20common%2C%20they're%20getting%20less%20popular.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.surveymonkey.com%2Fcuriosity%2Fdating-apps-and-sites-are-almost-as-common-as-they-are-disliked%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EA%20growing%20number%20ofAmericans%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20dislike%20the%20apps%2C%20with%20the%20ratings%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pewresearch.org%2Fshort-reads%2F2023%2F02%2F02%2Fkey-findings-about-online-dating-in-the-u-s%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Enotably%20lower%20for%20women%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20but%20a%20majority%20of%20single%20people%20still%20use%20them.%20And%20while%20dating%20companies%20have%20been%20raking%20in%20billions%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessofapps.com%2Fdata%2Fdating-app-report%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Emore%20than%20%245%20billion%20in%202023%20alone%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20growth%20is%20slowing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20turns%20out%20dating%20apps%20face%20a%20unique%20barrier%20to%20success%3A%20The%20more%20effective%20your%20app%20is%2C%20the%20less%20profitable%20it%20becomes.%20People%20pay%20to%20find%20a%20partner%2C%20and%20once%20you%20find%20one%2C%20the%20app%20loses%20your%20business.%20Sure%2C%20many%20seek%20ethical%20nonmonogamy%20or%20to%20cheat%2C%20but%20that's%20a%20niche%20market.%20The%20leading%20nonmonogamous%2C%20kink-positive%20dating%20app%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffeeld.co%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EFeeld%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20reached%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.macrotrends.net%2Fstocks%2Fcharts%2FMTCH%2Fmatch-group%2Frevenue%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%2435%20million%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20annual%20revenue%20this%20summer.%20Match%20Group%20earns%20100%20times%20as%20much.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDating%20apps%20are%20designed%20to%20be%20a%20miserable%20experience%2C%26quot%3B%20Stephanie%20Rodgers%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20the%20forthcoming%20dating%20app%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fverb.dating%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EVerb%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said.%20They%20%26quot%3Bhave%20little%20incentive%20to%20make%20dating%20more%20efficient%20%E2%80%94%20they%20need%20people%20to%20fail%20in%20order%20to%20get%20them%20to%20spend%20more%20money%20(and%20time)%20on%20the%20apps%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%20Rodgers%20seeks%20to%20avoid%20her%20competitors'%20fate%20of%20constant%20customer%20churn%20with%20a%20platform%20for%20planning%20both%20dates%20when%20single%20and%20date%20nights%20when%20partnered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20what%20my%20friends%20and%20I%20feel%3A%20manipulation%20by%20software%20whose%20goal%20is%20to%20keep%20you%20just%20interested%20enough%20to%20swipe%20but%20make%20it%20hard%20to%20find%20a%20lasting%20partner.%20That's%20the%20painful%20paradox%20of%20online%20dating.%20I've%20met%20so%20many%20of%20the%20people%20I%20love%20there%2C%20but%20the%20app%20draws%20out%20that%20process%20as%20long%20as%20it%20can%20to%20boost%20Match%20Group's%20profits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIncreasingly%2C%20it%20feels%20like%20dating%20apps%20make%20things%20more%20monotonous%20and%20cumbersome%20to%20incentivize%20us%20to%20pay%20for%20upgrades.%20They're%20like%20an%20airline%20that%20makes%20basic%20economy%20as%20awful%20as%20possible%20to%20twist%20our%20arms%20so%20we%20buy%20business%20class.%20Some%20apps%2C%20like%20Raya%2C%20cloak%20themselves%20in%20an%20air%20of%20exclusivity%2C%20screening%20applicants%20with%20unspecified%20criteria%20that%20are%20adjudicated%20by%20an%20anonymous%20review%20committee.%20The%20effect%20helps%20make%20members%20feel%20like%20it's%20a%20privilege%20to%20pay%20the%20high%20monthly%20membership%20fee.%20(Full%20disclosure%3A%20My%20own%20Raya%20application%20languished%20on%20their%20waitlist.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20visible%20gamification%20comes%20from%20Hinge%2C%20which%20markets%20itself%20as%20%26quot%3Bdesigned%20to%20be%20deleted.%26quot%3B%20But%20Hinge's%20reality%20varies%20widely%20from%20the%20sales%20pitch.%20Hinge%20lets%20you%20swipe%20on%20your%20algorithmically%20generated%20list%20of%20%26quot%3Bcompatible%26quot%3B%20users.%20But%20it%20also%20markets%20a%20second%20tab%20of%20%26quot%3Bstandout%26quot%3B%20profiles%20the%20algorithm%20thinks%20you'll%20like%20even%20more.%20But%20swiping%20on%20these%20locked%20profiles%20requires%20sending%20a%20digital%20%26quot%3Brose%26quot%3B%20that%20Hinge%20sells%20for%20up%20to%20%245%20apiece.%20Frustrated%20users%20nickname%20this%20tab%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2Fdiscover%2FWhat-is-rose-jail-hinge%3Flang%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ERose%20Jail%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20complaining%20that%20you'll%20never%20delete%20the%20app%20if%20you're%20walled%20off%20from%20the%20people%20you%20really%20want%20to%20run%20away%20from%20digital%20dating%20with.%20And%20even%20worse%2C%20often%20those%20in%20%26quot%3BRose%20Jail%26quot%3B%20don't%20actively%20use%20the%20app%2C%20meaning%20that%20Hinge%20makes%20you%20pay%20to%20send%20a%20message%20it%20knows%20will%20likely%20never%20be%20seen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20while%20dating%20apps'%20cost%20in%20terms%20of%20harassment%2C%20threats%2C%20and%20violence%20is%20paid%20disproportionately%20by%20women%2C%20its%20financial%20cost%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pewresearch.org%2Fshort-reads%2F2023%2F02%2F02%2Fkey-findings-about-online-dating-in-the-u-s%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eis%20disproportionately%20paid%20by%20men%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Increasingly%2C%20we're%20left%20feeling%20invisible%20if%20we%20don't%20pay.%20It%20can%20be%20both%20demoralizing%20and%20expensive.%20I%20found%20my%20own%20dating-app%20budget%20swinging%20wildly%20with%20my%20mood.%20Feeling%20lonely%20or%20sad%2C%20I%20might%20pay%20%245%20or%20%2410%20to%20%26quot%3Bboost%26quot%3B%20my%20profile%2C%20looking%20for%20added%20visibility%20and%20validation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20found%20myself%20boosting%20my%20self-esteem%20after%20a%20dismal%20date%20in%20September.%20After%20briefly%20bantering%20with%20an%20Upper%20East%20Side%20writer%20on%20Tinder%2C%20we%20planned%20for%20cocktails%20in%20midtown.%20Something%20was%20off%20when%20we%20texted%20to%20confirm%20the%20day%20of%2C%20especially%20the%20curt%20%26quot%3BOk%26quot%3B%20when%20I%20texted%20I%20was%20running%20five%20minutes%20late.%20I%20sprinted%20from%20Grand%20Central%2C%20hoping%20I%20wouldn't%20overheat%20in%20my%20cream-colored%20sweater%2C%20arriving%20exactly%20at%206%20after%20all.%20Our%20entire%20date%20was%20this%3A%20I%20said%20it%20was%20nice%20to%20see%20her.%20She%20stared%20at%20me%20blankly.%20I%20joked%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20been%20one%20of%20those%20chaotic%20workdays%20where%20I%20could%20use%20a%20cocktail%2C%20if%20you%20know%20what%20I%20mean%3F%26quot%3B%20Visibly%20upset%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BNo%2C%20I%20don't%2C%20and%20I'm%20not%20going%20to%20waste%20either%20of%20our%20time.%26quot%3B%20She%20left%20me%20stunned%20on%20the%20couch%2C%20next%20to%20her%20%2413%20sparkling%20water.%20When%20I%20paid%20for%20her%20bottle%2C%20the%20check%20said%206%3A03.%20I%20honestly%20will%20never%20understand%20what%20happened.%20On%20the%20train%20retreating%20back%20to%20Brooklyn%20bruised%20and%20bemused%2C%20I%20paid%20for%20every%20boost%20I%20saw.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20dating-app%20subscriptions%20aren't%20that%20much%20on%20their%20own%2C%20but%20add%20%2410%20to%20%2430%20a%20month%20for%20unlimited%20swipes%2C%20a%20litany%20of%20gamified%20add-ons%2C%20and%20it%20all%20adds%20up.%20In%20one%20month%2C%20altogether%2C%20the%20cost%20could%20easily%20be%20hundreds%20of%20dollars%20%E2%80%94%20not%20the%20cost%20of%20going%20on%20dates%2C%20not%20the%20cost%20of%20getting%20to%20know%20someone%2C%20but%20the%20cost%20of%20simply%20bribing%20the%20app%20to%20let%20me%20be%20seen.%20In%20the%20end%2C%20I'm%20just%20a%20boy%2C%20swiping%20on%20a%20girl%2C%20bribing%20the%20algorithm%20to%20like%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20expect%20this%20vicious%20business%20cycle%20to%20be%20a%20dating-app%20disaster%20in%20the%20long%20run.%20The%20more%20these%20platforms%20charge%2C%20the%20more%20people%20will%20leave%2C%20and%20the%20more%20people%20leave%2C%20the%20more%20desperate%20dating%20sites%20will%20be%20to%20charge%20even%20more.%20In%20its%20most%20recent%20annual%20report%2C%20Match%20Group%20highlighted%20that%20it%20boosted%20profits%20in%20the%20Americas%20by%207%25.%20But%20the%20company%20actually%20lost%207%25%20of%20its%20paying%20customers%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20and%20it%20made%20up%20for%20that%20only%20by%20charging%20the%20remaining%20users%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20more%20and%20more%20singles%20getting%20increasingly%20fed%20up%20with%20the%20apps%2C%20there's%20a%20surge%20of%20interest%20in%20alternatives.%20In%20my%20Brooklyn%20neighborhood%2C%20I%20constantly%20see%20ads%20taped%20to%20streetlights%20and%20buildings%20for%20dating%20meetups.%20Singles%20running%20clubs%20saw%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usatoday.com%2Fstory%2Flife%2Fhealth-wellness%2F2024%2F07%2F16%2Fsingles-run-club-new-york-relationships-dating%2F74369819007%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ehuge%20turnouts%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20runs%20where%20single%20runners%20wore%20a%20designated%20color.%20I've%20even%20tried%20speed%20dating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnalog%20alternatives%20are%20a%20wonderful%20change%20of%20pace%20from%20the%20apps'%20cold%20efficiency.%20Still%2C%20it's%20hard%20to%20go%20back%20after%20swiping.%20Apps%20give%20us%20so%20many%20options%20that%20we%20often%20build%20up%20a%20laundry%20list%20of%20what%20we%20need%20for%20compatibility.%20%26quot%3BDating%20apps%20invite%20idealizations%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20Weber%20puts%20it.%20%26quot%3BReal%20life%20is%20messier.%26quot%3B%20Meeting%20in%20person%2C%20we%20learn%20so%20much%20that%20can't%20be%20captured%20in%20a%20dating%20profile%2C%20but%20I%20still%20find%20it%20so%20much%20harder.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESoul-sucking%20as%20the%20apps%20are%2C%20I%20still%20love%20my%20love%20life%20and%20I'm%20still%20swiping.%20Even%20if%20I%20feel%20at%20war%20with%20the%20algorithms%20trying%20to%20shake%20me%20down%2C%20I'm%20amazed%20at%20the%20incredible%20people%20I%20meet.%20It's%20costly%20and%20exhausting%2C%20but%20it's%20still%20my%20best%20way%20to%20connect.%20And%20as%20I've%20grown%20older%20and%20my%20focus%20has%20progressed%20from%20casual%20dating%20to%20love%2C%20to%20building%20lasting%20partnership%20and%20family%2C%20I%20still%20find%20myself%20swiping%20the%20same%20apps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20week%20ago%2C%20I%20woke%20up%20grumpy%20from%20a%20bad%20date%20and%20the%20misguided%20swiping%20afterward%20and%20went%20for%20a%20run%20to%20try%20to%20shake%20it%20off.%20About%20a%20mile%20in%2C%20a%20vision%20of%20my%20younger%20self%20looking%20at%20my%20l