eating%20like%20that%20for%20weeks%20at%20a%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELuca's%20usual%20breakfast%20in%20Spain%20is%20fruit%20and%20sometimes%20cereal%2C%20but%20not%20the%20sugary%20kinds%20I%20had%20growing%20up%20in%20the%20US.%20He's%20always%20excited%20about%20donuts%20as%20soon%20as%20we%20arrive%20in%20the%20US%2C%20often%20wanting%20to%20find%20some%20as%20soon%20as%20we%20get%20to%20the%20airport.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Spain%2C%20meals%20are%20more%20balanced%2C%20with%20three-course%20lunches%20at%20school%20and%20healthier%20snacks%20throughout%20the%20day.%20There's%20almuerzo%2C%20a%20mid-morning%20snack%2C%20and%20merienda%2C%20an%20afternoon%20snack%20that%20often%20includes%20something%20sweet%20or%20savory.%20In%20California%2C%20it's%20usually%20just%20three%20main%20meals%20a%20day%2C%20with%20dessert%20being%20something%20sweet%20like%20ice%20cream%20or%20cookies.%20Luca's%20more%20accustomed%20to%20having%20yogurt%20or%20fruit%20after%20dinner%20in%20Spain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f3a0c357-ec17-45fc-8817-c2f044d96372%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHe%20also%20notices%20that%20everything%20in%20the%20US%20happens%20much%20earlier%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20US%2C%20everything%20happens%20much%20earlier%20than%20what%20we're%20used%20to%20in%20Spain.%20On%20weekends%20in%20Spain%2C%20we%20might%20start%20with%20breakfast%20around%208%20a.m.%2C%20have%20a%20snack%20around%2011%20a.m.%2C%20lunch%20at%202%20or%203%20p.m.%2C%20another%20snack%20around%206%20p.m.%2C%20and%20dinner%20as%20late%20as%209%20p.m.%20But%20in%20California%2C%20the%20day%20starts%20much%20earlier%20%E2%80%94%20breakfast%20can%20be%20as%20early%20as%207%20a.m.%2C%20lunch%20at%20noon%2C%20and%20dinner%20by%206%20p.m.%2C%20with%20everyone%20going%20to%20bed%20around%208%20p.m.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELuca%20definitely%20notices%20how%20different%20the%20routine%20is.%20In%20Spain%2C%20our%20schedule%20is%20more%20relaxed%20and%20flexible%2C%20especially%20with%20dinner%20and%20bedtime%2C%20which%20often%20depend%20on%20our%20social%20plans.%20In%20California%2C%20his%20cousins%20have%20a%20more%20structured%20day%2C%20with%20set%20meal%20times%20and%20early%20bedtimes%2C%20which%20is%20a%20big%20change%20for%20him.%20He's%20usually%20staying%20up%20later%20than%20his%20cousins%2C%20but%20because%20he's%20jet%20lagged%2C%20he's%20still%20in%20bed%20earlier%20than%20in%20Spain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2296094f01-9015-41c6-b0cb-d90bd8c8c37e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECalifornia's%20cold%20water%20is%20a%20big%20change%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20our%20last%20trip%20to%20California%2C%20my%20brother%20and%20father%20got%20stung%20by%20a%20stingray%20while%20we%20were%20at%20the%20beach.%20Luca%20had%20been%20having%20a%20great%20time%20in%20the%20ocean%20until%20that%20happened%2C%20but%20after%20that%2C%20he%20didn't%20want%20to%20go%20back%20into%20the%20water.%20It's%20so%20different%20from%20what%20he's%20used%20to%20with%20the%20Mediterranean%20Sea%2C%20where%20the%20water%20is%20warm%2C%20calm%2C%20and%20clear%20in%20the%20summer%2C%20making%20it%20feel%20very%20safe.%20We%20do%20have%20jellyfish%20in%20Spain%2C%20but%20they're%20easy%20to%20spot%20since%20they%20float%20on%20the%20surface.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20California%2C%20the%20water%20is%20much%20colder%2C%20and%20the%20waves%20are%20bigger%2C%20which%20is%20already%20a%20big%20change%20for%20him.%20But%20finding%20out%20there%20were%20stingrays%20hiding%20in%20the%20sand%20really%20shook%20him.%20Now%2C%20he's%20pretty%20much%20decided%20he%20never%20wants%20to%20go%20back%20into%20that%20ocean%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20all%20felt%20a%20bit%20uneasy%20after%20the%20stingray%20incident%2C%20especially%20since%20you%20can't%20see%20them.%20The%20kids%20there%20even%20do%20what%20they%20call%20the%20'stingray%20shuffle'%20to%20avoid%20stepping%20on%20them%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20exactly%20fun.%20Plus%2C%20getting%20out%20of%20that%20cold%20water%20and%20feeling%20freezing%20isn't%20something%20he's%20used%20to%2C%20especially%20compared%20to%20the%20warm%2C%20inviting%20beaches%20in%20Spain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-surprises-my-spanish-son-when-we-visit-the-us-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727947802000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f6a99bf9f6733e4be032e4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-surprises-my-spanish-son-when-we-visit-the-us-2024-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jennison%20Grigsby's%20son%20is%20almost%209.%20He's%20surprised%20about%20how%20sugary%20breakfast%20is%20in%20the%20US%20compared%20to%20Spain%2C%20and%20how%20everything%20happens%20earlier.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Jennifer%20Fern%C3%A1ndez%20Solano)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A30%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-surprises-my-spanish-son-when-we-visit-the-us-2024-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India's%20top%20court%20saves%20a%20poor%20student's%20college%20dream%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727947487000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F3975%2Flive%2F8dca78a0-8153-11ef-9775-fb5a546120c2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcx25nq12n10o%231%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Atul%20Kumar%20missed%20the%20deadline%20to%20pay%20his%20college%20fee%20by%20a%20few%20seconds%20-%20then%20a%20court%20stepped%20in%20to%20help%20him.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcx25nq12n10o%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcx25nq12n10o.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fn