erve%20To%20Be%20Rs%2018%20Crore%20Player%26quot%3B%3F%20MI%20Asked%20Blunt%20Question%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%202025%20auction%20will%20be%20a%20much%20followed%20affair.%20This%20time%20it's%20a%20mega%20auction%2C%20that%20means%20the%2010%20franchises%20will%20have%20to%20go%20the%20extra%20length%20at%20the%20planning%20table%20about%20which%20players%20they%20would%20want%20to%20retain.%20%26quot%3BThe%20IPL%20franchises%20can%20retain%20a%20total%20of%206%20players%20from%20their%20existing%20squad.%20This%20can%20be%20either%20via%20retention%20or%20by%20using%20the%20Right%20to%20Match%20(RTM)%20option.%C2%A0It%20is%20at%20the%20discretion%20of%20the%20IPL%20franchise%20to%20choose%20their%20combination%20for%20Retentions%20and%20RTMs.%20The%206%20retentions%20%2F%20RTM's%20can%20have%20a%20maximum%20of%205%20capped%20players%20(Indian%20%26amp%3B%20Overseas)%20and%20a%20maximum%20of%202%20uncapped%20players.%20The%20auction%20purse%20for%20the%20franchises%20has%20been%20set%20at%20INR%20120%20Crore%20for%20IPL%202025%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20BCCI%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20five-time%20champions%20Mumbai%20Indians%2C%20which%20finished%20last%20at%20the%20IPL%202024%2C%20it%20will%20be%20crucial%20season.%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Hardik%20Pandya%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64177-hardik-himanshu-pandya-playerprofile%5C%22%3EHardik%20Pandya%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20a%20much-discussed%20captaincy%20change.%20The%20team%20is%20star-studded%20with%20other%20players%20like%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Jasprit%20Bumrah%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1724-jasprit-bumrah-playerprofile%5C%22%3EJasprit%20Bumrah%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20tit