is-shaping-the-future-of-education-2017-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etechnology%20at%20school%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20But%20I%20also%20realized%20that%20by%20removing%20the%20thing%20that%20was%20challenging%20(the%20computer)%2C%20I%20was%20creating%20a%20whole%20set%20of%20new%20challenges.%20Since%20I'm%20not%20in%20the%20classroom%2C%20I%20probably%20didn't%20even%20know%20what%20some%20of%20those%20unintended%20consequences%20were.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20wife%20and%20I%20didn't%20know%20what%20the%20right%20answer%20was%20and%20didn't%20claim%20to%2C%20so%20we%20asked%20for%20a%20meeting%20with%20the%20school.%20My%20son%20has%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-adult-adhd-autism-diagnosis-changed-life-neurodivergent-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eautism%20and%20ADHD%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20so%20he%20has%20an%20individualized%20education%20program%20(IEP).%20That%20gave%20us%20a%20big%20advantage%20because%20the%20school%20had%20to%20listen%20to%20our%20concerns.%20Plus%2C%20we%20already%20had%20an%20established%20means%20of%20communicating%20with%20them%20and%20trust%20with%20my%20son's%20educational%20team.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22268895a0-ca6e-4701-8f44-b4586ba9427b%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20realized%20we%20needed%20a%20fluid%20approach%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20home%2C%20we%20could%20simply%20lock%20up%20computers%20and%20phones%20when%20our%20son%20had%20reached%20his%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbroke-parenting-rules-allowed-unlimited-screen-time-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Escreen%20time%20limit%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20For%20school%2C%20we%20knew%20it%20wouldn't%20necessarily%20be%20as%20simple.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInstead%2C%20we%20came%20to%20his%20teachers%20with%20a%20statement%3A%20We%20want%20to%20limit%20his%20access%20to%20his%20computer%20as%20much%20as%20possible%20while%20still%20supporting%20his%20learning.%20We%20asked%20what%20sorts%20of%20other%20systems%20we%20could%20implement%20within%20that%20framework.%20The%20details%20varied%20from%20class%20to%20class.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22318d14a9-c34a-4d8b-adbe-91924dac3017%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20went%20back%20to%20paper%20and%20pencil%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhenever%20possible%2C%20my%20son%20did%20his%20assignments%20with%20paper%20and%20pencil.%20For%20math%20problems%20or%20essay%20writing%2C%20this%20was%20fine.%20Yet%20we%20soon%20found%20there%20were%20assignments%20he%20simply%20couldn't%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudents-caught-using-chatgpt-ai-assignment-teachers-debate-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edo%20without%20a%20computer%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%94%20like%20watching%20a%20given%20video%20and%20writing%20a%20response.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20those%20situations%2C%20my%20son%20got%20access%20to%20his%20computer%2C%20with%20monitoring.%20For%20most%20of%20the%20day%2C%20his%20computer%20stayed%20in%20the%20resource%20teacher's%20room%2C%20and%20he%20only%20got%20it%20when%20he%20absolutely%20needed%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22071fcc00-5e80-434d-9d3b-5992a6ebccd8%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EImplementing%20this%20was%20hard%2C%20but%20worth%20it%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20knew%20reducing%20the%20reliance%20on%20tech%20at%20school%20wouldn't%20be%20easy%2C%20yet%20I%20was%20still%20surprised%20at%20just%20how%20difficult%20it%20was.%20We%20had%20a%20huge%20advantage%3A%20because%20of%20my%20son's%20IEP%2C%20we%20had%20a%20resource%20teacher%20we%20could%20always%20reach%20out%20to.%20Even%20so%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-screen-t