se%20violating%20orders%20of%20the%20Commission%20for%20Air%20Quality%20Management%2C%20tasked%20with%20tackling%20air%20pollution%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverybody%20knows%20that%20except%20discussion%20nothing%20is%20happening.%20That%20is%20the%20harsh%20reality%20of%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20AS%20Oka%20said.%20The%20bench%20also%20comprised%20Justice%20A%20Amanullah%20and%20Justice%20AG%20Masih.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20the%20court%20had%20asked%20the%20CAQM%20to%20file%20an%20affidavit%2C%20detailing%20the%20steps%20it%20had%20taken%20to%20combat%20stubble%20burning%2C%20among%20the%20key%20reasons%20behind%20Delhi's%20bad%20air%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Additional%20Solicitor%20General%20Aiswarya%20Bhati%20took%20the%20court%20through%20the%20composition%20of%20the%20panel%2C%20Justice%20Oka%20noted%20that%20the%20committee%20met%20only%20thrice%20in%20the%20past%20nine%20months%20and%20there%20was%20no%20discussion%20on%20stubble%20burning%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20last%20meeting%20was%20on%20August%2029.%20Entire%20September%2C%20there%20was%20no%20meeting.%20You%20said%20that%20this%20committee%20consists%20of%20IPS%20officers%20etc%20who%20will%20enforce%20the%20directions.%20Now%20not%20a%20single%20meeting%20has%20been%20held%20after%20August%2029%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20enforcement%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Oka%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Amanullah%20asked%20why%2011%20members%20skilled%20a%20meeting%20of%20a%20sub-committee%20on%20safeguarding%20and%20enforcement.%20%26quot%3BIs%20this%20the%20seriousness%20which%20is%20being%20shown%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Oka%20said%20only%20some%20meetings%20were%20being%20held.%20%26quot%3BWhere%20is%20the%20implementation%20on%20the%20grassroots%20level%20of%20your%20orders%3F%20Unless%20there%20is%20prosecution%2C%20nobody%20is%20going%20to%20bother%20about%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20government's%20counsel%20replied%20that%20they%20had%20registered%20FIRs%20under%20the%20section%20relating%20to%20disobedience%20of%20orders%20of%20a%20public%20servant%2C%20the%20court%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20taken%20the%20softest%20provision%20that%20is%20there%20to%20prosecute.%20There%20is%20Section%2014%20of%20CAQM%20Act%2C%20Section%2015%20of%20the%20Environmental%20Protection%20Act%20which%20has%20drastic%20powers.%26quot%3B%20The%20government%20counsel%20said%20they%20did%20not%20take%20drastic%20measures%20because%20the%20air%20pollution%20levels%20had%20come%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20must%20implement%20your%20own%20orders.%20This%20is%20all%20in%20the%20air.%20There%20are%20targets%2C%20action%20plans%2C%20sectoral%20meetings%20but%20the%20basic%20provisions%20of%20the%20Act%20are%20not%20be%20implemented%20at%20all.%20In%202024%2C%20there%20are%20129%20cases%20of%20stubble%20burning%2C%20why%20action%20has%20not%20been%20taken%20against%20these%20people%3F%20Why%20Section%2015%20of%20the%20Environmental%20Protection%20Act%20is%20not%20invoked%20and%20why%20the%20corresponding%20action%20is%20not%20taken%20against%20the%20officers%20of%20the%20government%3F%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Oka%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20noted%20that%20nominal%20compensation%20had%20been%20imposed%20on%20those%20found%20to%20be%20burning%20crop%20stubble.%20%26quot%3BHolding%20meetings%20will%20not%20serve%20any%20purpose%20unless%20at%20the%20grassroots%20level%2C%20you%20show%20that%20action%20has%20been%20taken.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20discussion%20then%20shifted%20to%20machines%20that%20can%20be%20used%20to%20remove%20crop%20stubble%20so%20that%20the%20fields%20are%20not%20set%20afire.%20The%20Punjab%20government's%20lawyer%20submitted%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20problem%20is%20the%20machine%20is%20available%2C%20it%20is%20being%20given%20free%20of%20cost%20to%20the%20farmer%20who%20wants%20to%20use%20it.%20The%20farmer%20is%20not%20being%20able%20to%20use%20it%20because%2070%20per%20cent%20of%20farmers%20in%20Punjab%20have%20less%20than%2010%20acres%20of%20land.%20(He)%20will%20have%20to%20employ%20a%20driver%20and%20use%20diesel%20in%20that%20machine%20which%20they%20are%20not%20willing%20to%20do.%26quot%3B%20The%20state%20proposed%20that%20the%20farmers%20be%20provided%20the%20cost%20of%20running%20these%20machines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20then%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BSo%20you%20are%20trying%20to%20tell%20us%20that%20we%20will%20do%20nothing%20unless%20we%20get%20money%20from%20the%20central%20government%20of%20India%3F%20Unless%20penal%20action%20starts%20at%20the%20grassroots%20level%2C%20this%20issue%20will%20not%20be%20resolved...%20There%20is%20no%20fear.%20Machines%20are%20there%20but%20they%20are%20not%20going%20to%20use%20the%20machines.%20It%20is%20as%20simple%20as%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727944980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fslao08do_delhi-air-pollution-_625x300_03_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-air-pollution-harsh-reality-is-nothing-is-happening-top-court-on-delhi-air-pollution-6706251%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20harsh%20reality%20is%20that%20nothing%20substantial%20was%20being%20done%20to%20address%20the%20air%20pollution%20problem%20choking%20Delhi%20every%20year%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-air-pollution-harsh-reality-is-nothing-is-happening-top-court-on-delhi-air-pollution-6706251%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Everyone%20go%20thank%20Usha'%3A%20Viral%20post%20credits%20JD%20Vance's%20'Indian%20wife'%20for%20his%20impressive%20debate%20performance%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727944978000%2C%22visual%22%3A%