o%20get%20a%20result.%20I%20know%20the%20result%20could%20have%20gone%20either%20way%20but%20I%20was%20ok%20with%20it%20%2C%20so%20was%20the%20coach%20and%20the%20other%20players.%20You%20have%20to%20be%20brave%20enough%20to%20take%20those%20decisions%20and%20go%20and%20play%20that%20way.%20When%20things%20fall%20in%20place%2C%20everything%20looks%20good%20and%20that%20is%20where%2C%20it%20can%20change%20very%20quickly%20when%20things%20don't%20fall%20in%20place.%20Everybody%20would%20have%20started%20criticising%20the%20decision%20we%20took%20and%20all%20of%20that.%20But%20what%20matters%20is%20what%20we%20think%20inside%20this%20changing%20room%20and%20that%20is%20what%20matters%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20bowlers%20came%20to%20the%20party%20first%2C%20got%20wickets%20we%20needed%2C%20when%20we%20came%20inside%2C%20we%20had%20to%20take%20risk%20and%20the%20result%20could%20have%20gone%20on%20either%20side%20but%20I%20was%20okay%20with%20it%20and%20so%20was%20the%20coach%2C%20because%20you%20have%20to%20be%20brave%20enough%20to%20take%20certain%20decisions%20and%20also%20play%20that%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20clear%20plan%20that%20we%20want%20a%20result%20and%20how%20we%20can%20get%20that%20result%20and%20everybody%20started%20finding%20answers%20for%20that.%20I%20think%20this%20was%20an%20exceptional%20series%20that%20may%20go%20unnoticed%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20skipper%20felt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%20was%20very%20pleased%20with%20fielding%20as%20the%20team%20took%2023%20out%20of%20the%2024%20catches%20that%20came%20its%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20just%20informed%2C%2024%20catches%20came%20our%20way%20and%20we%20took%2023%2C%20great%20result%2C%20especially%20in%20India%20where%20ball%20doesn't%20carry%20in%20slips%20and%20because%20they%20were%20standing%20way%20ahead%20than%20they%20normally%20do.%20The%20catches%20are%20hard%20to%20take%20as%20reaction%