e%20all%20the%20women-centric%20films%20passed%20the%20test.%20This%20ties%20in%20with%20the%20%E2%80%98male%20gaze%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20the%20objectification%20of%20women%20in%20cinema%20%E2%80%94%20that%20many%20hypermasculine%20Bollywood%20films%20are%20guilty%20of.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20we%20asked%20Bakshi%20if%20it%E2%80%99s%20tough%20navigating%20morally%20right%20ground%20while%20also%20attempting%20to%20tell%20a%20story%20that%20appeals%20to%20an%20audience.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20the%20director%E2%80%99s%20discretion%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20asserts.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20easy%20to%20veer%20towards%20cheap%20headlines%20when%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F166082%2Frajasthan-pregnant-womenr-undercover-agents%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20covering%20burning%20issues%3C%2Fa%3E.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20sensitising%20the%20audience%20is%20tough%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E50%20countries%20pledge%20for%20a%20safer%20%26amp%3B%20equitable%20world%20at%20the%20screening%20of%20Vibha%20Bakshi%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Son%20Rise%E2%80%99%20%40expo2020dubai%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2Fnzpavilion%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23nzpavilion%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FIndiaPavilion%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23IndiaPavilion%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FUNHub%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23UNHub%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWomensPavilion%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WomensPavilion%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Funwomenindia%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40unwomenindia%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2F