she%20shares.%20While%20she%20could%20very%20well%20have%20chosen%20a%20narrative%20that%20was%20fodder%20for%20controversy%2C%20she%20decided%20to%20look%20instead%20towards%20the%20radical%20changes%20the%20judiciary%20was%20implementing.%20She%20decided%20to%20tell%20a%20story%20of%20hope%20and%20courage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98When%20it%20gets%20scary%2C%20persist%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20%3Cem%3Ekhap%20panchayat%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20North%20India%20sees%20hundreds%20of%20men%20%E2%80%94%20staunch%20patriarchs%20%E2%80%94%20gather%20to%20pass%20the%20verdict%20on%20%E2%80%98important%20issues%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20murders%2C%20property%20disputes%2C%20and%20elections%20to%20the%20constitutional%20bodies.%20%3Cem%3EDowry%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20social%20evil)%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F340672%2Fjharkhand-farming-rukmani-devi-abusive-marriage-domestic-violence-survivor-learnt-farming-to-earn-income%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edomestic%20violence%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20female%20foeticide%20do%20not%20feature%20in%20the%20mix.%20Smokescreens%20for%20bolstering%20patriarchy%2C%20these%20%3Cem%3Ekhap%20panchayats%3C%2Fem%3E%20are%20arenas%20where%20men%20have%20the%20final%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20when%20Bakshi%20stood%20face%20to%20face%20with%20a%20battalion%20of%20men%2C%20with%20the%20strapping%20%3Cem%3Ekhap%3C%2Fem%3E%20leader%20at%20the%20fore%2C%20her%20worst%20fears%20were%20realised.%20%E2%80%9CI%20knew%20I%20was%20bad%20news%20here.%20It%20dawned%20on%20me%20that%2C%20as%20a%20woman%2C%20I%20had%20just%20entered%20the%20seat%20of%20patriarchy.%20The%20%3Cem%3Ekhap%20%3C%2Fem%3Eleader%20was%20not%20welcoming%20to%20being%20questioned.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20then%20she%20treats%20me%20to%20a%20fun%20fact.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20ended%20up%20becoming%20one%20of%20our%20main%20heroes%20in%20the%20film.%E2%80%9D%3C%2