day%20paused%20a%20Madras%20High%20Court%20order%2C%20asking%20Tamil%20Nadu%20police%20to%20investigate%20cases%20filed%20against%20spiritual%20leader%20Sadhguru's%20Isha%20Foundation.%20The%20top%20court%20transferred%20the%20case%20to%20itself%20and%20asked%20the%20police%20to%20file%20a%20status%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%2C%20led%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%2C%20was%20hearing%20Isha%20Foundation's%20challenge%20against%20the%20high%20court%20order%2C%20following%20which%20hundreds%20of%20police%20personnel%20entered%20Isha%20Foundation's%20premises%20in%20Coimbatore%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court's%20direction%20came%20after%20retired%20professor%20S%20Kamaraj%20filed%20a%20petition%2C%20alleging%20that%20his%20two%20daughters%20Geeta%20and%20Lata%20were%20%26quot%3Bbrainwashed%20to%20reside%20at%20Isha%20Yoga%20Centre%26quot%3B%20in%20Coimbatore.%20He%20alleged%20that%20the%20foundation%20did%20not%20allow%20them%20to%20maintain%20any%20contact%20with%20their%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsha%20Foundation%20has%20denied%20the%20allegations%20and%20said%20the%20two%20women%20--%20aged%2042%20and%2039%20--%20had%20been%20staying%20at%20the%20foundation's%20premises%20willingly.%20The%20two%20women%20were%20also%20produced%20in%20the%20high%20court%2C%20where%20they%20confirmed%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsha%20Foundation%20also%20said%20the%20petitioner%20and%20others%20tried%20to%20trespass%20into%20the%20premises%20under%20the%20pretext%20of%20being%20members%20of%20a%20fact-finding%20committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHearing%20the%20matter%2C%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20noted%20that%20a%20doctor%20at%20the%20Foundation's%20Ashram%20was%20recently%20charged%20with%20child%20abuse%20under%20the%20stringent%20POCSO%20Act%20and%20said%20the%20probe%20must%20continue.%20Senior%20Advocate%20Mukul%20Rohatgi%2C%20appearing%20for%20Isha%20Foundation%2C%20said%20the%20alleged%20incidents%20did%20not%20happen%20on%20its%20campus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Justice%20then%20asked%20if%20the%20two%20women%20were%20online%20so%20that%20the%20bench%2C%20also%20comprising%20Justice%20JB%20Pardiwala%2C%20could%20speak%20to%20them.%20Mr%20Rohatgi%20said%20they%20were.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Justice%20then%20noted%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20first%20thing%20is%20that%20you%20cannot%20let%20an%20army%20of%20police%20in%20the%20establishment%20like%20this...%20what%20we%20will%20do%20is%20ask%20a%20judicial%20officer%20to%20visit%20the%20premises%2C%20and%20talk%20to%20these%20two%20inmates.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20women%20appeared%20before%20the%20court%20virtually%20and%20reiterated%20that%20they%20were%20at%20the%20ashram%20willingly.%20She%20alleged%20that%20their%20father%20had%20been%20harassing%20them%20for%20the%20past%20eight%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENoting%20that%20this%20was%20a%20habeus%20corpus%20petition%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20would%20like%20to%20hear%20both%20monks%20in%20the%20chamber%20and%20come%20back%20in%20five%20minutes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Justice%20later%20said%20the%20women%20had%20told%20them%20that%20they%20joined%20the%20Ashram%20when%20they%20were%2024%20and%2027%2C%20respectively%2C%20and%20were%20living%20there%20willingly.%20The%20court%20also%20noted%20that%20the%20mother%20of%20the%20two%20women%20had%20filed%20a%20similar%20petition%20eight%20years%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727937840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fmpb9kue_mastering-the-art-of-handling-unpleasant-memories-sadhguru_625x300_01_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcops-to-stop-probe-supreme-court-pauses-high-court-order-against-sadhguru-6705624%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20paused%20a%20Madras%20High%20Court%20order%2C%20asking%20Tamil%20Nadu%20police%2