reported%20wealth%20as%20they%20head%20to%20the%20polls%20in%20November.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fwhat-are-donald-trump-kamala-harris-jd-vance-and-tim-walz-worth-13225105%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fwhat-are-donald-trump-kamala-harris-jd-vance-and-tim-walz-worth-13225105%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fwhat-are-donald-trump-kamala-harris-jd-vance-and-tim-walz-worth-13225105%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Once%20Punished%20for%20Her%20Deafness%2C%20Rupmani%20Chhetri%20Now%20Empowers%20Thousands%20With%20the%20Signable%20App%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%20in%20Darjeeling%2C%20Rupmani%20Chhetri%2C%20the%2037-year-old%20co-founder%20of%20SignAble%20Communications%2C%20felt%20a%20deep%20sense%20of%20loneliness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Rupmani%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20child%2C%20I%20believed%20that%20I%20was%20the%20only%20Deaf%20person%20in%20the%20world.%20With%20no%20awareness%20of%20sign%20language%2C%20I%20experienced%20discrimination%20with%20various%20labels%20placed%20on%20me%20because%20of%20my%20Deafness.%20I%20was%20excluded%20from%20family%20activities%20and%20conversation%20and%20struggled%20in%20school%2C%20as%20teachers%20would%20speak%20and%20I%20could%20not%20hear.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20no%20adequate%20school%20for%20the%20Deaf%20in%20Darjeeling%20at%20the%20time%2C%20Rupmani%E2%80%99s%20father%2C%20a%20security%20guard%2C%20spent%20whatever%20he%20could%20to%20put%20her%20in%20a%20regular%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEfforts%20to%20express%20myself%20through%20sign%20language%20were%20met%20with%20punishment%20from%20teachers%20who%20failed%20to%20recognise%20my%20disability.%20Since%20I%20was%20a%20Deaf%20child%2C%20I%20felt%20isolated%20and%20unheard.%20My%20early%20education%20was%20mostly%20just%20copying%20notes%20without%20understanding%20concepts%2C%20except%20for%20geography%2C%20which%20I%20found%20more%20accessible%20due%20to%20its%20visual%20nature%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20extended%20family%20was%20convinced%20that%20I%20would%20never%20succeed%20academically%20and%20saw%20the%20process%20of%20educating%20me%20as%20a%20futile%20effort.%20By%20the%20time%20I%20was%209%20or%2010%2C%20I%20had%20to%20start%20working%20to%20cover%20the%20costs%20of%20my%20school%20essentials.%20Making%20matters%20worse%2C%20I%20was%20also%20forced%20into%20speech%20therapy%2C%20as%20there%20was%20no%20access%20to%20sign%20language%20available%20to%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FSignAble-Communicate-with-kids-1727526887.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Helping%20the%20Deaf%20to%20communicate.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FSignAble-Communicate-with-kids-1727526887.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FSignAble-Communicate-with-kids-1727526887-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FSignAble-Communicate-with-kids-1727526887-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FSignAble-Communicate-with-kids-1727526887-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FSignAble-Communicate-with-kids-1727526887-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-367955%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHelping%20the%20Deaf%20to%20communicate.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20Rupmani%E2%80%99s%20incredible%20struggles%20early%20on%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20remarkable%20that%20years%20later%20she%20would%20go%20on%20to%20co-found%20a%20venture%20called%20SignAble%20Communications%2C%20which%20among%20other%20things%2C%20has%20developed%20an%20app%20that%20provides%20a%20video%20relay%20service%20that%20empowers%20the%20Deaf%20to%20communicate%20and%20express%20themselves%20without%20barriers.%20The%20app%20offers%20Deaf%20persons%20%E2%80%9Caccess%20to%20a%20live%20interpreter%20at%20their%20fingertips%2C%20anytime%20and%20anywhere%2C%20all%20at%20an%20affordable%20price%E2%80%9D%2C%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThanks%20to%20the%20app%2C%20Deaf%20people%20can%20communicate%20with%20essential%20service%20providers%20like%20the%20police%20and%20doctors%2C%20while%20also%20allowing%20them%20to%20communicate%20with%20their%20family%20and%20work%20colleagues.%20Here%E2%80%99s%20the%20remarkable%20story%20of%20how%20she%20found%20herself%20and%20developed%20an%20app%20which%20is%20helping%20open%20up%20different%20worlds%20for%20thousands%20of%20Indians%20who%20cannot%20hear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDiscovering%20her%20identity%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20studying%20up%20till%20Class%209%2C%20she%20got%20married%20to%20her%20Deaf%20partner%20and%20they%20moved%20to%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20initially%20saw%20marriage%20as%20a%20way%20to%20address%20my%20challenges%20and%20start%20anew%2C%20which%20led%20me%20to%20move%20to%20Delhi.%20After%20facing%20numerous%20difficulties%20in%20the%20relationship%2C%20I%20made%20the%20difficult%20decision%20to%20return%20home%20but%20my%20family%20didn%E2%80%99t%20approve%20and%20insisted%20that%20I%20needed%20to%20figure%20things%20out%20on%20my%20own%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%20It%20was%20only%20after%20her%20divorce%20in%202011%20that%20Rupmani%20resumed%20her%20studies%20and%20went%20on%20to%20finish%20high%20school.%20She%20would%20go%20on%20to%20earn%20a%20bachelor%E2%80%99s%20degree%20in%20sociology.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLiving%20in%20Delhi%20ultimately%20provided%20me%20with%20the%20opportunity%20to%20connect%20with%20other%20Deaf%20individuals%20in%20my%20early%20twenties%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20the%20first%20time%20I%20witnessed%20sign%20language%20being%20used%20among%20the%20Deaf%20community.%20I%20longed%20to%20join%20them%2C%20but%20they%20often%20excluded%20me%20because%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20sign%20language%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThankfully%2C%20she%20found%20resources%20developed%20by%20organisations%20like%20the%20Noida%20Deaf%20Society%20(NDS)%20and%20%E2%80%98The%20Way%20Deaf%E2%80%99%20to%20learn%20sign%20language%2C%20supplemented%20by%20various%20YouTube%20videos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F334578%2Fcoda-child-of-deaf-adult-indian-sign-language-isl%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESign%20language%20is%20the%20native%20language%20of%20the%20Deaf%20community%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20allowing%20individuals%20to%20express%20themselves%20and%20communicate%20authentically%2C%20just%20like%20anyone%20else.%20It%20is%20a%20fundamental%20right%2C%20and%20access%20to%20it%20should%20be%20provided%20from%20a%20young%20age%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20argues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssisting%20her%20during%20this%20time%20in%20Delhi%20were%20disability%20rights%20activists%20like%20Geeta%20Sharma%20of%20the%20National%20Association%20of%20the%20Deaf%20(NAD)%20and%20the%20late%20Javed%20Abidi%20from%20the%20National%20Centre%20for%20Promotion%20of%20Employment%20for%20Disabled%20People%20(NCPEDP)%20who%20she%20believes%20played%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpivotal%20role%20in%20helping%20me%20discover%20the%20true%20essence%20of%20knowledge%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20introduced%20me%20to%20the%20Deaf%20community%20and%20other%20specially-abled%20communities%20and%20provided%20invaluable%20guidance%20that%20has%20empowered%20me%20to%20navigate%20the%20world%20with%20confidence.%20I%20am%20deeply%20grateful%20for%20their%20support%20during%20this%20crucial%20phase%20of%20my%20life%3B%20without%20their%20mentorship%2C%20I%20would%20have%20felt%20lost.%20Through%20their%20encouragement%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F101036%2Fdelhi-cafe-hearken-hearing-impaired-staff%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EI%20learned%20sign%20language%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20forged%20meaningful%20friendships%2C%20and%20embarked%20on%20a%20transformative%20journey%20to%20discover%20my%20own%20identity%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20brief%20stint%20with%20the%20NAD%2C%20she%20began%20working%20with%20HAQ%3A%20Centre%20for%20Child%20Rights%2C%20a%20Delhi-based%20non-profit.%20Her%20nearly%20six-year%20stint%20at%20HAQ%20landed%20her%20an%20opportunity%20to%20work%20with%20the%20United%20Nations%20Development%20Programme%20(UNDP)%20in%202017%20in%20Europe%20where%2C%20among%20other%20things%2C%20she%20discovered%20the%20transformative%20impact%20of%20Video%20Relay%20Service%20(VRS)%20for%20the%20Deaf.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20blog%20published%20on%20the%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.unv.org%2Fdiversity-mosaic-inspirations%2Frupmani-chhetri-personifying-nothing-impossible%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20UN%20Volunteers%20website%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CMotivated%20to%20bring%20a%20change%2C%20Rupmani%20started%20her%20UN%20Volunteer%20journey%20with%20the%20aim%20of%20establishing%20a%20cross-cultural%20dialogue%20and%20exchange%20of%20knowledge%20between%20Ukraine%20and%20India.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20Communications%20Assistant%2C%20she%20%E2%80%9Csupported%20the%20internally%20displaced%20people%20of%20the%20war%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2Fvideo%2Fi-decided-to-become-a-special-educator-and-to-help-disabled-people-communicate-in-sign-language%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econducted%20sign%20language%20courses%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20teenagers%20and%20adults%20with%20hearing%20impairment%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CShe%20did%20the%20same%20for%20UN%20colleagues%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20Germany%20and%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20further%20said%20in%20the%20blog.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FRupmani-Chhetri-Pic-1727526989.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rupmani%20Chhetri%2C%20co-founder%20of%20SignAble%20Communications.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FRupmani-Chhetri-Pic-1727526989.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FRupmani-Chhetri-Pic-1727526989-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FRupmani-Chhetri-Pic-1727526989-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FRupmani-Chhetri-Pic-1727526989-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FRupmani-Chhetri-Pic-1727526989-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-367956%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERupmani%20Chhetri%2C%20co-founder%20of%20SignAble%20Communications.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThrough%20the%20war%2C%20some%20people%20had%20acquired%20disabilities%20or%20become%20injured%2C%20including%20around%20300%20Deaf%20people%20who%20had%20become%20displaced.%20They%20were%20asking%20me%2C%20as%20a%20fellow%20Deaf%20person%2C%20for%20help.%20I%20was%20not%20aware%20of%20how%20to%20help%2C%20so%20I%20had%20a%20lot%20to%20learn%2C%20especially%20how%20to%20deal%20with%20post-traumatic%20stress%20disorder.%20Deaf%20people%20wanted%20to%20tell%20me%20their%20stories%20and%20what%20they%20went%20through.%20By%20being%20able%20to%20communicate%20with%20me%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20give%20them%20a%20message%20of%20love%20and%20reassurance%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20told%20UN%20Volunteers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20her%20one-and-a-half-year%20stint%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20Rupmani%20also%20took%20part%20in%20multiple%20initiatives%20with%20other%20UN%20agencies%20%E2%80%94%20including%20the%20Office%20of%20the%20United%20Nations%20High%20Commissioner%20for%20Human%20Rights%20(OHCHR)%2C%20United%20Nations%20Children%E2%80%99s%20Fund%20(UNICEF)%2C%20and%20the%20United%20Nations%20Refugee%20Agency%20(UNHCR).%20It%20was%20a%20truly%20rewarding%20time%20for%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20she%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CDespite%20facing%20numerous%20discouragements%2C%20I%20made%20it%20a%20point%20to%20embrace%20life%20as%20a%20series%20of%20risks%2C%20willing%20to%20try%20anything%20that%20came%20my%20way.%20I%20moved%20to%20Ukraine%20and%20travelled%20across%20Europe%2C%20where%20I%20was%20amazed%20by%20the%20robust%20access%20to%20sign%20language%20in%20other%20countries%2C%20especially%20the%20availability%20of%20technology%20like%20VRS.%20This%20exposure%20allowed%20me%20to%20learn%20and%20grow%20in%20ways%20I%20had%20never%20imagined.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESignAble%20for%20the%20Deaf%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20her%20time%20in%20Europe%2C%20Rupmani%20came%20back%20to%20India.%20While%20looking%20for%20a%20job%2C%20she%20encountered%20Tarun%20Sarwal%2C%20who%20also%20returned%20to%20India%20after%20spending%20more%20than%20a%20decade%20working%20with%20humanitarian%20organisations%20in%20Europe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20first%20met%20Mr%20Tarun%20while%20I%20was%20looking%20for%20a%20job%20after%20returning%20from%20my%20work%20at%20the%20UN.%20A%20common%20friend%20introduced%20us%20online%2C%20and%20during%20our%20initial%20conversations%2C%20Tarun%20asked%20how%20I%20could%20contribute%20to%20supporting%20people%20with%20disabilities.%20After%20many%20discussions%20about%20potential%20projects%20and%20ideas%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20meet%20in%20person.%20Our%20first%20face-to-face%20meeting%20took%20place%20on%201%20January%2C%202019%2C%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20amidst%20the%20Deaf%20community.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20during%20his%20time%20working%20in%20Geneva%20with%20an%20international%20humanitarian%20organisation%20that%20Tarun%20was%20inspired%20by%20the%20difference%20an%20interpreter%20could%20make%20in%20a%20Deaf%20person%E2%80%99s%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FSignAble-Communications-Team-1727527431.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22SignAble%20Communications%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FSignAble-Communications-Team-1727527431.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FSignAble-Communications-Team-1727527431-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FSignAble-Communications-Team-1727527431-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FSignAble-Communications-Team-1727527431-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.theb