0zero-waste%20initiatives%20to%20three%20neighbouring%20villages.%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F218884%2Fbengaluru-couple-grow-organic-vegetable-balcony-zero-waste-tips-inspiring-india-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewe%20went%20zero%20waste%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20was%20just%20a%20few%20months%20into%20operations%2C%20the%20dumping%20of%20plastic%20waste%20gradually%20stopped%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20walk%20down%20a%20once-nameless%20village%20bordering%20Tieedi%2C%20I%20am%20greeted%20by%20an%20enthusiastic%20man%20weaving%20a%20bamboo%20basket%20outside%20his%20house.%20The%20village%20has%20come%20to%20be%20known%20as%20Naya%20Basti%20(translates%20to%20%E2%80%98new%20village%E2%80%99)%20and%20is%20located%20near%20Gorabari%2C%20bordering%20Sonada.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20Utsow%20%3Cem%3Ebhai%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20doing%20is%20truly%20amazing%2C%E2%80%9D%20Badal%20Chettri%2C%2061%2C%20tells%20me.%20Weaving%20baskets%20is%20something%20he%20does%20to%20pass%20the%20time%20since%20his%20retirement%2C%20and%20his%20products%20find%20their%20way%20into%20neighbouring%20shops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20won%E2%80%99t%20find%20any%20plastic%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20Badal%20says%20with%20pride%2C%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20might%20be%20a%20little%20plastic%20near%20a%20construction%20site%20on%20top.%20But%20we%E2%80%99ve%20asked%20the%20workers%20to%20gather%20all%20of%20it%20in%20one%20place%3B%20we%E2%80%99ll%20collect%20and%20send%20it%20to%20the%20waste%20facility%20soon.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-09-27-at-19.05.27_11zon-1727444189.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Badal%20Chet