E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20burning%20desire%20to%20pursue%20her%20passion%20and%20share%20her%20art%20with%20the%20world%2C%20Varsha%20uploaded%20her%20first%20video.%20What%20began%20as%20short%20dance%20and%20comedy%20clips%20soon%20evolved%20into%20something%20bigger.%20But%20every%20coin%20has%20two%20sides.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20she%20faced%20harsh%20mockery%20and%20trolls%20hiding%20behind%20their%20screens%2C%20trying%20to%20pull%20her%20down.%20Varsha%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20one%20to%20give%20up%20easily.%20She%20flipped%20the%20coin%20%E2%80%94%20and%20her%20story.%20Her%20content%20began%20to%20gain%20traction%2C%20and%20soon%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F255612%2Fsocial-media-influencer-instagram-senior-citizens-mr-mrs-verma-yashpal-singh-shanta-jonita-haryana-trends-online-collaboration-romance-old-age-boredom-lockdown-inspirational-vid01%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eher%20videos%20began%20going%20viral%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20laughed%20at%20me%20at%20first%2C%E2%80%9D%20Varsha%20shared.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20then%20something%20incredible%20happened.%20My%20videos%20started%20to%20take%20off%2C%20and%20suddenly%2C%20people%20were%20following%20my%20journey.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20talent%20and%20charm%20earned%20her%20a%20spot%20on%20the%20popular%20dance%20reality%20show%20%3Cem%3EDance%20Deewane%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20where%20she%20wowed%20both%20the%20judges%20and%20the%20audience.%20One%20of%20the%20judges%20told%20her%2C%20%E2%80%9CYou%E2%80%99re%20a%20real%20hero.%20People%20need%20to%20learn%20from%20you.%20You%20didn%E2%80%99t%20let%20life%20drown%20you%20%E2%80%94%20you%20fought%20back.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20an%20emotional%20moment%20on%20the%20show%2C%20she%20reflected%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20used%20to%20dream%20about%20this%2C%20but%20never%20thought%20it%20could%20happen.%20Life%20has%20a%20funny%20way%20of%20giving%20you%20a%20second%20chance.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20with%205.8%20million%20followers%2C%20Varsha%20is%20living%20proof%20that%20an%20undying%20passion%20can%20take%20you%20to%20places%20you%20never%20even%20imagined.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727446429000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D367863%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Born%20into%20poverty%2C%20Varsha%20Solanki%20worked%20as%20a%20domestic%20help%20while%20nurturing%20a%20lifelong%20passion%20for%20dance.%20After%20marriage%20and%20motherhood%2C%20she%20turned%20to%20social%20media%20to%20rekindle%20her%20art%2C%20going%20viral%20and%20reaching%20five%20million%20followers.%20Here's%20her%20story.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Khushi%20Arora%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A41%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F367863%2Fvarsha-solanki-social-media-sensation-reality-show-dance-deewane-story-watch-domestic-help-dancer-video%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Heart%20Attack%20Symptoms%20In%20Women%3A%20Spotting%20the%20Hidden%20Signs%20%26amp%3B%20How%20They%20Are%20Different%20For%20Women%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHeart%20disease%20is%20commonly%20misconstrued%20as%20a%20problem%20associated%20primarily%20with%20men%2C%20but%20studies%20have%20shown%20that%20it%20is%20far%20from%20the%20truth.%20A%20lack%20of%20awareness%2C%20research%2C%20and%20prevention%20efforts%20has%20resulted%20in%20women%20often%20silently%20suffering%20from%2C%20and%20dying%20of%2C%20preventable%20heart%20diseases.%20This%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F317906%2Fhow-to-prevent-heart-attack-detect-cardiac-symptoms-ecg-device-sanketlife-rahul-neha-rastogi-noida%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWorld%20Heart%20Day%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20we%20aim%20to%20shift%20the%20narrative%20to%20the%20often-ignored%20subject%20of%20women%E2%80%99s%20heart%20health.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELife%20was%20routine%20for%2040-year-old%20Neha%20until%20an%20incident%20shook%20her%20world.%20The%20Haridwar%20resident%20started%20experiencing%20sudden%20dizziness%20and%20fainting%20episodes%2C%20blacking%20out%20for%20a%20few%20seconds%20before%20regaining%20consciousness.%20This%20happened%20four%20to%20five%20times%20over%20two%20days.%20She%20visited%20a%20local%20doctor%20who%20advised%20her%20to%20immediately%20seek%20treatment%20from%20a%20specialist%20in%20Dehradun.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20conducting%20ECGs%20and%20other%20basic%20tests%2C%20the%20doctor%20in%20Dehradun%20realised%20that%20these%20were%20symptoms%20of%20sudden%20cardiac%20arrests%20and%20referred%20her%20to%20the%20Fortis%20Escorts%20Heart%20Institute%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20where%20she%20proceeded%20for%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Aparna%20Jaswal%2C%20Director%20of%20Cardiology%2C%20Department%20of%20Cardiac%20Pacing%20and%20Electrophysiology%20at%20Fortis%2C%20identified%20Neha%E2%80%99s%20symptoms%20as%20a%20heart%20ailment%2C%20explaining%20that%20her%20sudden%20fainting%20episodes%20were%20the%20result%20of%20cardiac%20arrest.%20They%20were%20able%20to%20identify%20the%20ailment%20through%20continuous%20heart%20monitoring.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeha%E2%80%99s%20case%20is%20not%20the%20only%20one.%20The%20prevalence%20of%20coronary%20artery%20diseases%20in%20women%20range%20from%20three%20to%2013%20percent%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3EJournal%20of%20the%20American%20College%20of%20Cardiology%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20report%20also%20states%20that%20the%20disease%20has%20increased%20by%20over%20300%20percent%20in%20the%20past%2020%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Global%20Burden%20of%20Disease%20Study%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F341755%2Fcongenital-heart-disease-in-babies-treatment-surgery-provided-by-hans-foundation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eheart%20disease%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20leading%20cause%20of%20fatality%20among%20Indian%20women%2C%20accounting%20for%20over%2017%20percent%20of%20deaths.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20alarming%20statistic%20underscores%20the%20importance%20of%20recognising%20the%20unique%20ways%20heart%20diseases%20manifest%20in%20women%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20critical%20need%20for%20awareness%20and%20proactive%20health%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHeart%20disease%20is%20the%20biggest%20killer%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHeart%20disease%20refers%20to%20a%20range%20of%20conditions%20like%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F336492%2Fgoan-artist-xavier-fernandes-makes-christmas-cribs-from-driftwood%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecoronary%20artery%20disease%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20congenital%20heart%20disease%2C%20arrhythmia%20(irregular%20heartbeats)%2C%20cardiac%20arrest%2C%20and%20more.%20It%20is%20one%20of%20the%20leading%20causes%20of%20death%20worldwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20more%20often%20than%20not%2C%20heart%20diseases%20are%20preventable%20and%20can%20be%20successfully%20treated%20if%20diagnosed%20early.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20traditional%20belief%20is%20that%20heart%20diseases%20generally%20affect%20women%2010%20years%20later%20than%20men%2C%20this%20is%20no%20longer%20the%20case.%20Just%20like%20younger%20men%20are%20getting%20heart%20attacks%2C%20so%20are%20women%2C%20but%20they%20are%20often%20unaware%20of%20the%20signs%20and%20symptoms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fheart-care-1040227_1280-1727414916.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fheart-care-1040227_1280-1727414916.jpg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fheart-care-1040227_1280-1727414916-300x212.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fheart-care-1040227_1280-1727414916-500x354.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fheart-care-1040227_1280-1727414916-768x543.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fheart-care-1040227_1280-1727414916-150x106.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-367768%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22905%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20doctors%2C%20the%20first%20vital%20step%20is%20to%20address%20a%20common%20misconception%20that%20cardiovascular%20diseases%2C%20including%20heart%20attacks%2C%20affect%20men%20more%20than%20women.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20critical%20difference%20is%20that%20women%20often%20experience%20%E2%80%98silent%E2%80%99%20heart%20diseases%2C%20where%20symptoms%20may%20not%20be%20as%20pronounced%20or%20may%20be%20misattributed%20to%20other%20conditions.%20This%20often%20leads%20to%20delays%20in%20diagnosis%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Ravinder%20Singh%20Rao%2C%20interventional%20structural%20cardiologist%2C%20chairman%20at%20RHL%20Center%2C%20Jaipur%2C%20and%20consultant%20at%20Lilavati%20Hospital%20and%20Research%20Centre%2C%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETherefore%2C%20it%20is%20imperative%20for%20women%20to%20be%20aware%20of%20the%20symptoms%20and%20to%20seek%20immediate%20hospital%20care%20whenever%20they%20experience%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESymptoms%20of%20a%20heart%20attack%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20usual%20symptoms%20common%20across%20genders%20include%20chest%20pain%2C%20pressure%20or%20discomfort%20that%20lasts%20more%20than%20a%20few%20minutes%20or%20recurs%2C%20Dr%20Rao%20informs.%20However%2C%20he%20adds%20that%20chest%20pain%20experienced%20by%20women%20may%20differ%20slightly%20from%20that%20experienced%20by%20men%2C%20often%20described%20more%20as%20pressure%20or%20tightness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COther%20symptoms%20seen%20in%20women%20include%20neck%2C%20jaw%20and%20shoulder%20pain%2C%20shortness%20of%20breath%2C%20pain%20in%20one%20or%20both%20arms%2C%20nausea%20or%20vomiting%2C%20sweating%2C%20or%20dizziness.%20Women%20should%20be%20particularly%20cautious%20about%20atypical%20symptoms%2C%20as%20they%20may%20not%20be%20recognised%20as%20signs%20of%20a%20heart%20attack%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Jaswal%20adds%20that%20dizziness%2C%20blurring%20or%20fainting%2C%20radiating%20pain%20to%20the%20shoulders%20and%20jaw%2C%20extreme%20fatigue%20or%20breathlessness%2C%20and%20palpitations%20are%20also%20symptoms%20seen%20in%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCopy-of-Infographic-website-3-1727414804.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCopy-of-Infographic-website-3-1727414804.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCopy-of-Infographic-website-3-1727414804-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCopy-of-Infographic-website-3-1727414804-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCopy-of-Infographic-website-3-1727414804-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCopy-of-Infographic-website-3-1727414804-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-367765%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E(Symptoms%20from%20the%20World%20Heart%20Federation)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20informs%20that%20earlier%2C%20hormones%20were%20believed%20to%20provide%20protection%20against%20heart%20diseases%20till%20menopause%2C%20when%20the%20levels%20dropped.%20However%2C%20that%20is%20not%20the%20case%20today%2C%20as%20younger%20women%2C%20too%2C%20experience%20heart%20ailments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERisk%20factors%20include%20high%20blood%20pressure%2C%20high%20cholesterol%2C%20diabetes%2C%20smoking%2C%20and%20a%20family%20history%20of%20heart%20disease.%20If%20you%20have%20any%20of%20these%2C%20you%20should%20get%20regular%20check-ups.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEvery%20adult%2C%20be%20it%20a%20woman%20or%20a%20man%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F288854%2Ftamil-nadu-auto-driver-daughter-tops-board-exams-after-fathers-heart-attack%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emust%20get%20yearly%20check-ups%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Check%20your%20blood%20pressure%20and%20sugar%2C%20especially%20if%20you%20have%20a%20family%20history%20of%20heart%20disease.%20If%20any%20of%20these%20levels%20are%20elevated%2C%20treat%20them%20on%20time.%20Heart%20diseases%20are%20preventable%20if%20these%20risk%20factors%20are%20in%20check%20and%20monitored%20regularly%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Jaswal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditional%20risk%20factors%20for%20women%20include%20pregnancy%20complications.%20If%20a%20woman%20has%20gestational%20diabetes%20or%20preeclampsia%20(high%20blood%20pressure)%2C%20the%20risk%20of%20heart%20disease%20later%20increases.%20Therefore%2C%20doctors%20stress%20that%20it%20is%20vital%20for%20women%20of%20all%20ages%20to%20prioritise%20their%20heart%20health.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20World%20Heart%20Federation%2C%20women%20also%20tend%20to%20have%20more%20severe%20first%20heart%20attacks%20that%20more%20frequently%20lead%20to%20death%20compared%20to%20men.%20%E2%80%9CWomen%20are%20the%20forefront%20and%20backbone%20of%20the%20family.%20Yet%2C%20they%20quietly%20die%20due%20to%20sudden%20cardiac%20arrests%2C%20and%20not%20much%20is%20spoken%20about%20it.%20It%E2%80%99s%20time%20that%20women%20recognise%20the%20warning%20signs%20and%20rush%20to%20the%20hospital%20any%20time%20they%20experience%20any%20of%20the%20symptoms%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Jaswal%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20urges%20women%20to%20have%20yearly%20health%20check-ups%20and%20take%20immediate%20action%20if%20any%20of%20their%20levels%20are%20high.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeha%E2%80%99s%20prompt%20thinking%20probably%20saved%20her%20life.%20You%20too%20can%20save%20yours%20by%20taking%20care%20of%20your%20health%20and%20acting%20promptly.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTime%20is%20critical%20during%20a%20heart%20attack%2C%20and%20even%20a%20minute%20can%20turn%20the%20situation%20around%20for%20a%C2%A0%20person.%20In%20crucial%20times%2C%20you%20should%20trust%20your%20instincts%2C%20and%20if%20something%20feels%20wrong%2C%20you%20should%20immediately%20seek%20medical%20attention%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Rao.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727419891000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fheart-care-1040227_1280-1727414916.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D367755%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Heart%20disease%20manifests%20differently%20in%20women%20and%20is%20an%20oft%20ignored%20subject.%20We%20spoke%20to%20doctors%20who%20explained%20the%20different%20symptoms%20women%20experience%20and%20the%20warning%20signs%20that%20must%20not%20be%20ignored.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F367755%2Fworld-heart-day-heart-disease-heart-attack-women-symptoms-warning-signs-cardiologists%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Kamal%20Malik%20Restored%20Asia%E2%80%99s%20Oldest%20Ice%20Factory%20%26amp%3B%20Turned%20it%20Into%20IF.BE%20in%20Mumbai%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUnsure%20of%20what%20to%20do%20in%20Mumbai%20this%20weekend%3F%20Here%E2%80%99s%20an%20idea%3A%20Take%20a%20trip%20to%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20south%2C%20the%20plush%20neighbourhood%20of%20Ballard%20Estate%20in%20particular.%20As%20you%20walk%20down%20Calicut%20Road%20%E2%80%93%20a%20street%20named%20after%20the%20traders%20from%20Calicut%20(present-day%20Kozhikode)%20who%20settled%20in%20the%20city%20%E2%80%93%20you%20are%20likely%20to%20see%20a%20two-storeyed%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F358205%2Ftiny-farm-fort-homestay-rishikesh-raghav-ansh-kumar-delhi-architects-cob-sustainable-home%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Earchitectural%20marvel%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20IF.BE.%20What%20began%20its%20journey%20as%20an%20ice%20factory%20in%201878%2C%20now%20serves%20as%20a%20space%20for%20creative%20minds%20to%20discuss%20art%20and%20ideas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20IF.BE%20isn%E2%80%99t%20hosting%20a%20stand-up%20show%20by%20comedian%20Masoom%20Rajwani%2C%20it%20finds%20itself%20overwhelmed%20by%20cinema%20aficionados.%20Yes%2C%20the%20scramble%20for%20a%20front-row%20seat%20to%20director%20Zoya%20Akhtar%E2%80%99s%20session%20on%20storytelling%20is%20real.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20these%20maestros%20aren%E2%80%99t%20gracing%20the%20dais%2C%20there%20are%20meditative%20movement%20workshops%2C%20film%20screenings%20and%20art%20exhibitions%20to%20sign%20up%20for.%20IF.BE%E2%80%99s%20social%20calendar%20lives%20up%20to%20its%20definition%20of%20a%20space%20where%20architects%2C%20designers%20and%20artists%20can%20converge%20and%20collaborate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfi